s%2C%20her%20condition%20rapidly%20deteriorated.%20She%20experienced%20a%20series%20of%20alarming%20symptoms%2C%20including%20temporary%20blindness%2C%20a%20locked%20jaw%20and%20vomiting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20doesn't%20make%20sense%20why%20would%20you%20give%20someone%20a%20vaccines%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20is%20Alexis%20Lorenze%20at%20a%20medical%20centre%20in%20California%20-%20her%20disposition%20is%20a%20direct%20immediate%20consequence%20of%20being%20given%20Vaccines.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20World%20continues%20to%20awaken%20to%20the%20dangers%20of%20vaccination.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FZrlL0InTFu%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FZrlL0InTFu%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Concerned%20Citizen%20(%40BGatesIsaPyscho)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBGatesIsaPyscho%2Fstatus%2F1835881948960428376%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2017%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlexis%20Lorenze%20does%20not%20have%20health%20insurance%20in%20California.%20Now%2C%20she%20is%20being%20transferred%20to%20a%20private%20hospital%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20for%20specialised%20care%2C%20said%20a%20fundraiser%20raising%20money%20for%20her%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%2023-year-old's%20deteriorating%20condition%2C%20VSRF%20has%20sent%20Registered%20Nurse%20Angela%20Wulbrecht%20and%20a%20team%20of%20trusted%20doctors%20to%20assist%20with%20her%20care.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlexis%20Lorenze%20has%20been%20using%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20TikTok%20to%20detail%20her%20medical%20journey.%20Disturbing%20images%20and%20videos%20shared%20by%20Ms%20Lorenze%20reveal%20the%20severity%20of%20her%20alleged%20vaccine%20reaction.%20The%20visuals%20show%20her%20with%20swollen%20eyes%20and%20forehead%2C%20severe%20black-pur