%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYonder%20cofounders%20Harry%20Jell%2C%20Theso%20Jivajirajah%2C%20and%20Tim%20Chong.%3Cp%3EYonder%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EYonder%2C%20a%20London-based%20fintech%20startup%2C%20raised%20%2430.1%20million%20in%20new%20funding.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFounded%20in%202020%2C%20Yonder%20offers%20a%20credit%20card%20with%20rewards%20for%20a%20monthly%20fee.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20funding%20will%20expand%20the%20team%20and%20support%20European%20expansion%20plans.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYonder%2C%20a%20London-based%20fintech%20startup%2C%20has%20raised%20%2430.1%20million%20in%20new%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202020%20by%20former%20staffers%20at%20credit%20scoring%20startup%20Clearscore%2C%20Yonder%20offers%20users%20a%20credit%20card%20with%20rewards%20such%20as%20meals%20at%20high-end%20restaurants%2C%20tickets%20to%20events%2C%20and%20points%20toward%20flights.%20The%20startup%20charges%20a%20%C2%A315%20(around%20%2418.80)%20monthly%20subscription%20fee%20for%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20began%20by%20focusing%20on%20expats%20in%20the%20UK%20who%20didn't%20have%20a%20credit%20score%2C%20but%20it%20now%20caters%20to%20a%20wider%20market%20of%20non-expat%20customers%20living%20in%20cities%20like%20London%2C%20Manchester%2C%20Birmingham%2C%20Bristol%2C%20and%20Bath.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20really%20tough%20time%20for%20fundraising%20fintech%20startups%2C%20so%20we're%20super%20proud%20of%20the%20raise%20we've%20been%20able%20to%20secure%20in%20this%20climate%2C%26quot%3B%20Tim%20Chong%2C%20Yonder%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20haven't%20seen%20many%20consumer%20fintechs%20raise%20recently%2C%20especially%20at%20our%20stage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20most%20of%20them%20are%20at%20the%20pre-IPO%20or%20very%20early%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20funding%20was%20led%20by%20Repeat%20(formally%20Jigsaw)%20and%20RTP%20Global%2C%20plus%20existing%20investor%20Latitude%2C%20the%20sister%20fund%20of%20LocalGlobe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20follows%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyonder-london-fintech-startup-raises-new-funding-from-vc-investors-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20%2478%20million%20debt%20and%20equity%20raise%20in%20April%202023%2C%20led%20by%20Northzone%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Yonder%20claims%20its%20latest%20raise%20is%20a%20significant%20up%20round%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20post-money%20valuation%20of%20more%20than%20%24132%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20building%20for%20the%20long-term%20horizon%2C%20and%20we've%20generally%20found%20that%20investors%20who%20think%20long-term%20and%20are%20bullish%20in%20the%20space%20really%20get%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Chong%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20definitely%20tough%20though%20%E2%80%94%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20more%20focus%20on%20unit%20economics%2C%20payback%20times%2C%20and%20long-term%20profitability%20this%20time%20round.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20it%20will%20use%20the%20new%20funding%20to%20expand%20its%2045-strong%20team%20to%20around%2060%2C%20while%20aiming%20to%20keep%20head%20count%20lean%2C%20Chong%20said.%20In%20addition%2C%20Yonder%20said%20it's%20targeting%20European%20expansion%20and%20is%20keeping%20track%20of%20customer%20travel%20locations%20to%20decide%20on%20its%20next%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheck%20out%20Yonder's%2011-slide%20pitch%20deck%20below%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225334%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yonder%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eade72d17aa3c7b2b3aa90%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EYonder%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225334%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yonder%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.i