iness-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fsc-rejects-telecom-firms-pleas-in-agr-case-vi-shares-plunge-10-124091900495_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bitter%20divorce%2C%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20richest%20woman%20and%202%20dead%20in%20Moscow%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726730671000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113483407%2Cimgsize-700131.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fwho-is-russias-richest-woman-tatyana-bakalchuk-vladislav-wildberries%2Farticleshow%2F113483394.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20headquarters%20of%20Russia's%20largest%20online%20retailer%20Wildberries%20became%20the%20scene%20of%20violence%2C%20resulting%20in%20two%20deaths%20and%20seven%20injuries.%20The%20clash%20involved%20founder%20Tatyana%20Bakalchuk%20and%20her%20estranged%20husband%20Vladislav%20amid%20escalating%20tensions%20over%20a%20controversial%20merger%20with%20Russ.%20This%20incident%20has%20brought%20corporate%20disputes%20into%20sharp%20focus%20within%20Russia's%20business%20landscape.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fwho-is-russias-richest-woman-tatyana-bakalchuk-vladislav-wildberries%2Farticleshow%2F113483394.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBut%20Creative%20Freedom%3F%26quot%3B%20Censor%20Gets%20Deadline%20To%20Clear%20Kangana's%20'Emergency'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStressing%20that%20the%20trend%20of%20objecting%20to%20the%20release%20of%20films%20must%20stop%2C%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20today%20asked%20the%20Central%20Board%20of%20Film%20Certification%20(CBFC)%20to%20take%20a%20call%20on%20actor-MP%20Kangana%20Ranaut's%20movie%20Emergency%20by%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20was%20hearing%20a%20petition%20by%20the%20movie's%20co-producer%20Zee%20Entertainment%20Enterprises%2C%20seeking%20the%20release%20of%20the%20censor%20certificate%20so%20that%20the%20movie%20can%20hit%20the%20screens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20movie%2C%20which%20stars%20Kangana%20Ranaut%2C%20Anupam%20Kher%20and%20Shreyas%20Talpade%2C%20is%20based%20on%20the%20Emergency%20imposed%20by%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20government%20in%201975.%20It%20has%20run%20into%20trouble%20after%20Sikh%20organisations%20alleged%20that%20it%20misrepresents%20the%20community.%20Sources%20in%20the%20central%20government%20have%20said%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bsome%20sensitive%20content%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhinav%20Chandrachud%2C%20the%20censor%20board's%20counsel%2C%20told%20the%20court%20that%20its%20decision%20was%20based%20on%20representations%20objecting%20to%20the%20movie's%20release.%20He%20submitted%20that%20some%20scenes%20show%20a%20polarising%20figure%20cutting%20a%20deal%20with%20political%20parties.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20see%20whether%20this%20is%20factually%20accurate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20division%20bench%20of%20Justice%20BP%20Colabawalla%20and%20Justice%20Firdosh%20Pooniwalla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Colabawalla%20said%20'Emergency'%20is%20a%20movie%20and%20not%20a%20documentary.%20%26quot%3BDo%20you%20think%20that%20the%20public%20is%20so%20naive%20that%20they%20will%20believe%20everything%20they%20see%20in%20a%20movie%3F%20What%20about%20about%20creative%20freedom%3F%20It's%20not%20for%20CBFC%20to%20decide%20whether%20this%20affects%20public%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBFC%20said%20it%20must%20send%20the%20matter%20to%20a%20revising%20committee%20and%20asked%20for%20two%20weeks%20to%20decide%20the%20matter%2C%20but%20the%20court%20refused.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20enough%20time%20given%20to%20decide%20on%20either%20giving%20a%20certificate%20or%20rejecting%20it%2C%20but%20you%20only%20passed%20the%20buck%20that%20the%20review%20committee%20will%20decide%20or%20the%20revision%20committee%20will%20decide.%20Now%20you%20take%20a%20decision%20by%20Monday%20on%20(whether)%20you%20want%20to%20release%20or%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20CBFC%20%26quot%3Bcan't%20sit%20on%20the%20fence%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BTake%20a%20decision.%20Let's%20see%20what%20the%20revising%20commitee%20says%2C%20be%20it%20deciding%20to%20release%20or%20not%2C%20take%20a%20decision.%20Have%20the%20courage%20to%20say%20that%20the%20film%20should%20not%20be%20released.%20We%20will%20appreciate%20the%20stand%20of%20the%20CBFC%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20said%20the%20trend%20of%20objecting%20to%20the%20release%20of%20films%20needs%20to%20stop.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20about%20creative%20freedom%20and%20the%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20in%20our%20country%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20Zee%20counsel%20Venkatesh%20Dhond%20said%20CBFC%20was%20biding%20time%20with%20an%20eye%20on%20Haryana%20elections.%20The%20Censor%20responded%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bstate%20in%20question%20is%20Punjab%2C%20not%20Haryana%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20court%20asked%20what%20is%20the%20political%20angle%20in%20the%20case%2C%20Mr%20Chandrachud%20said%20there%20was%20none.%20But%20Mr%20Dhond%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20will%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20BJP%20MP%20(Kangana%20Ranaut)%20offending%20a%20community.%20The%20political%20apprehension%20is%20that%20the%20Sikh%20community%20will%20feel%20this%20film%20is%20anti-Sikh%2C%20CBFC%20is%20the%20executive%20and%20people%20won't%20vote%20for%20those%20who%20approved%20the%20release%20of%20the%20film%20which%20is%20anti-Sikh.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20producer%20is%20also%20part%20of%20the%20ruling%20party.%20So%20are%20you%20saying%20the%20ruling%20party%20wants%20to%20stop%20the%20release%20of%20a%20film%20of%20a%20member%20of%20its%20own%20party%3F%26quot%3B%20The%20court%20said%20it%20is%20not%20concerned%20with%20elections%20and%20noted%20that%20the%20financial%20burden%20of%20the%20film%20is%20huge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20matter%20came%20up%20before%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20when%20two%20Sikh%20organisations%20filed%20a%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation.%20In%20response%2C%20the%20Censor%20Board%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20movie%20had%20not%20been%20issued%20a%20certificate.%20The%20court%20then%20disposed%20of%20the%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Zee's%20counsel%20told%20the%20high%20court%20that%20CBFC%20had%20informed%20the%20filmmakers%20that%20the%20certificate%20was%20issued%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not%20handed%20over.%20The%20court%20today%20remarked%20that%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20was%20%26quot%3Btaken%20for%20a%20ride%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726730640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fuskevogo_kangana-emergency_625x300_04_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkangana-ranauts-emergency-cant-be-released-yet-censor-decision-in-a-week-6599688%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kangana%20Ranaut's%20'Emergency'%20Can't%20Be%20Released%20Yet%2C%20Censor%20Decision%20In%20A%20Week%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Morgan%20Stanley%20secures%20Rs%202%2C122%20cr%20office%20lease%20for%2016%20floors%20in%20Mumbai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726730014000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-02%2F15%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1707960430-2526.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fmorgan-stanley-secures-rs-2-122-cr-office-lease-for-16-floors-in-mumbai-124091900467_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20office%