e%20Dieux%20Deliverance%20Serum%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20use%20Dieux%20Deliverance%20Serum%3C%2Fh2%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20holds%20a%20bottle%20of%20the%20Dieux%20Deliverance%20Serum%20in%20their%20hand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eaa5c7ce3009a0fac71e0b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERebecca%20String%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Dieux%2C%20the%20Deliverance%20Serum%20is%20meant%20to%20be%20used%20twice%20daily%20for%20best%20results.%20However%2C%20the%20company%20notes%20that%20if%20you%20have%20sensitive%20skin%2C%20it's%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20start%20by%20using%20it%20nightly%20and%20then%20work%20up%20to%20twice%20a%20day%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20reaction.%20I%20didn't%20notice%20any%20issues%20within%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20after%20my%20first%20application%2C%20so%20I%20proceeded%20to%20use%20it%20twice%20daily.%20Something%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%3A%20It%20can%20take%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedlineplus.gov%2Fency%2Farticle%2F000869.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eup%20to%2048%20hours%20for%20an%20allergic%20reaction%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20appear%20on%20your%20skin%2C%20so%20you%20might%20want%20to%20wait%20two%20full%20days%20before%20you%20start%20using%20Deliverance%2C%20or%20any%20new%20product%2C%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20Dieux's%20recommendations%2C%20l%20applied%20it%20in%20between%20cleansing%20and%20moisturizing.%20I%20followed%20it%20up%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dee63a2ef780f4ab43faa08adcac5abc507f1c1071abc41a9c1613e0e220157b0%26postID%3D66eaa10058fda2320efacae4%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fbeauty%252Fdieux-deliverance-serum-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.dermalogica.com%252Fproducts%252Fdynamic-skin-recovery-spf50%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D