t%20and%20after%20using%20it%20on%20the%20right%2C%20my%20skin%20was%20noticeably%20less%20red%20after%20one%20week.%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Strong%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20I%20pumped%20this%20serum%20into%20my%20hand%2C%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20consistency.%20It%20has%20a%20lightweight%2C%20milky%2C%20and%20somewhat%20slippery%20feel%20on%20my%20fingers.%20Upon%20smoothing%20it%20over%20my%20face%20and%20neck%2C%20it%20left%20a%20dewy%20finish.%20It%20didn't%20feel%20sticky%20or%20tacky%20at%20all%2C%20gave%20me%20a%20non-greasy%20glow%2C%20and%20layered%20like%20a%20dream%20under%20moisturizer%20and%20makeup%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDieux%20reports%20that%20in%20an%20eight-week%20independent%2C%20third-party%20clinical%20study%2C%2094%25%20of%20people%20who%20applied%20the%20Deliverance%20serum%20once%20daily%20felt%20their%20skin%20was%20immediately%20smoother%20after.%20After%20four%20weeks%2C%20many%20participants%20noticed%20a%20significant%20decrease%20in%20fine%20lines%20and%20wrinkles%2C%20and%20after%20eight%20weeks%2C%20they%20saw%20an%20improvement%20in%20dark%20spots%20and%20uneven%20skin%20tone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Dieux%2C%20the%20main%20benefits%20that%20occur%20in%20the%20first%20few%20weeks%20of%20using%20Deliverance%20are%20skin%20soothing%20and%20calming%20%E2%80%94%20improvements%20in%20texture%20and%20tone%20tend%20to%20kick%20in%20after%20at%20least%20four%20to%20eight%20weeks%2C%20and%20the%20appearance%20of%20fine%20lines%20and%20wrinkles%20tend%20to%20fade%20after%2012%20weeks%20or%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20brace%20myself%20for%20a%20reaction%20whenever%20I%20introduce%20a%20new%20skincare%20product%20into%20my%20routine.%20Fortunately%2C%20I%20experienced%20no%20irritation%20while%20using%20the%20product%20%E2%80%94%20and%20better%20yet%2C%20my%20skin%20felt%20hydrated%2C%20smooth%2C%20and%20plump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2205952641-f29f-41bd-af00-d7a6a8e6de1d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20bottom%20line%5C%22%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUpon%20looking%20back%20at%20photos%20of%20my%20skin%20before%20using%20Deliverance%2C%20I%20did%20notice%20some%20pink%20undertones%20around%20my%20nose%20and%20cheeks%20%E2%80%94%20something%20I've%20struggled%20with%20my%20whole%20life%2C%20although%20I%20don't%20have%20full-blown%20rosacea.%20After%20using%20Deliverance%20for%20just%20one%20week%2C%20that%20pink%20flush%20was%20gone%2C%20and%20my%20skin%20definitely%20looked%20more%20even-toned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDid%20Deliverance%20dramatically%20transform%20my%20skin%3F%20No%2C%20but%20that%20would%20be%20unrealistic%20to%20expect%20in%20a%20one-week%20period.%20Did%20it%20deliver%20its%20promises%20to%20save%20me%20from%20redness%2C%20dryness%2C%20and%20irritation%3F%20Yes%2C%20it%20did.%20And%20for%20now%2C%20that's%20good%20enough%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226a523677-2f04-4d22-8eac-ac95f69b856e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFAQs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20a%20face%20serum%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESerums%20can%20range%20a%20lot%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20active%20ingredients%20and%20what%20skin%20concerns%20they%20address.%20Some%20serums%20are%20targeted%20to%20help%20brighten%20the%20skin%20and%20reduce%20dark%20spots%20and%20discoloration%2C%20while%20others%20are%20formulated%20to%20help%20shrink%20pore%20size%20or%20make%20wrinkles%20and%20fine%20lines%20less%20noticeable.%20Serums%20can%20be%20oil-%20or%20water-based%2C%20but%20they're%20highly%20concentrated%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20a%20little%20goes%20a%20long%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESerums%20have%20a%20few%20things%20in%20common%2C%20though.%20They're%20typically%20lightweight%20and%20easily%20absorbed%20by%20the%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20serum%20depends%20on%20your%20goals.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.health.harvard.edu%2Fblog%2Fskin-serum-what-it-can-and-cant-do-2018061214029%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHarvard%20Health%3C%2Fa%3E%20advises%20seeking%20serums%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fvitamin-c-for-skin%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evitamin%20C%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ferulic%20acid%2C%20and%20kojic%20acid%20to%20brighten%20the%20skin%20or%20lighten%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fhyperpigmentation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehyperpigmentation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20your%20skin%20is%20dry%20and%20flaky%2C%20try%20serums%20with%20vitamin%20E%2C%20niacinamide%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fhyaluronic-acid-benefits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehyaluronic%20acid%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Finally%2C%20if%20you%20want%20a%20serum%20with%20anti-aging%20benefits%2C%20look%20for%20formulas%20that%20contain%20antioxidants%20like%20resveratrol%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC3583892%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeptides%2C%20retinol%2C%20and%20niacinamide%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20causes%20skin%20irritation%E2%80%94and%20what%20ingredients%20can%20help%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EContact%20dermatitis%20is%20irritation%20and%20inflammation%20of%20the%20skin.%20There%20are%20two%20types%3A%20irritant%20contact%20dermatitis%20and%20allergic%20contact%20dermatitis.%20The%20former%20happens%20when%20irritating%20substances%20damage%20the%20skin%20cells%3B%20the%20latter%20is%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-of-allergic-reaction-food-environment-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eallergic%20reaction%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20typically%20leads%20to%20an%20itchy%20rash.%20Some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Farticle%2F10.1007%2Fs12016-018-8713-0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20common%20areas%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20symptoms%20of%20irritant%20contact%20dermatitis%20to%20appear%20include%20the%20cheeks%2C%20chin%2C%20near%20the%20corners%20of%20the%20nose%20and%20mouth%2C%20and%20the%20eyelids.%20A%20reaction%20can%20happen%20almost%20immediately%20or%20take%2024-48%20hours%20to%20develop%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mayoclinic.org%2Fdiseases-conditions%2Fcontact-dermatitis%2Fsymptoms-causes%2Fsyc-20352742%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIf%2520you%2520avoid%2520the%2520substance%2Cin%25202%2520to%25204%2520weeks.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecan%20last%20for%20up%20to%20two%20to%20four%20weeks%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20you%20stop%20using%20whatever%20caused%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFragrances%20and%20preservatives%20are%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmy.clevelandclinic.org%2Fhealth%2Fdiseases%2F6173-contact-dermatitis%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etop%20culprits%20of%20contact%20dermatitis%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20skincare%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20identifying%20and%20avoiding%20irritants%20that%20cause%20a%20reaction%20on%20your%20skin%2C%20you%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hopkinsmedicine.org%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-and-diseases%2Fcontact-dermatitis%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euse%20barrier%20creams%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20block%20out%20irritants.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhs.uk%2Fconditions%2Fcontact-dermatitis%2Ftreatment%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELook%20for%20products%20with%20emollients%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20glycerin%20and%20hyaluronic%20acid%2C%20which%20can%20attract%20moisture%20to%20the%20skin%20while%20preventing%20moisture%20from%20evaporating.%20Emollients%20can%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmy.clevelandclinic.org%2Fhealth%2Ftreatments%2F23305-emollients%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelp%20to%20soften%20and%20soothe%3C%2Fa%3E%20peeling%2C%20scaling%2C%20or%20flaking%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhen%20should%20you%20apply%20serum%20in%20your%20skincare%20routine%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20you%20know%20it%20or%20not%2C%20the%20order%20in%20which%20you%20apply%20your%20skincare%20products%20impacts%20how%20well%20your%20skin%20absorbs%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenerally%2C%20experts%20advise%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhealth.clevelandclinic.org%2Fproper-skin-care-product-order%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eapplying%20lightweight%20products%20first%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20heavier%20products%20last.%20That's%20because%20richer%20creams%20and%20other%20heavy%20products%20can%20form%20a%20barrier%20on%20the%20skin%20that%20may%20block%20the%20absorption%20of%20other%20ingredients%20in%20lightweight%20formulas.%20With%20that%20in%20mind%2C%20you%20should%20apply%20serums%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.health.harvard.edu%2Fblog%2Fskin-serum-what-it-can-and-cant-do-2018061214029%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eafter%20cleansing%20and%20toning%20but%20before%20moisturizing%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fdieux-deliverance-serum-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726729493000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eaa9abce3009a0fac71e74%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fdieux-deliverance-serum-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20put%20the%20Dieux%20Deliverance%20Serum%20to%20the%20test%20to%20see%20if%20it%20could%20revive%20my%20sensitive%2C%20irritated%20skin.%20The%20results%20were%20even%20better%20than%20expected.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Strong)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fdieux-deliverance-serum-review%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Salman%20Khan's%20father%20threatened%20with%20Bishnoi's%2