%20government%20Rs%2092%2C000%20crore%20within%20three%20months.%20The%20current%20petitions%20are%20against%20a%20September%202020%20order%20requiring%20payment%20of%20AGR%20dues%20over%20a%2010-year%20period%3B%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20by%20March%2031%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20petition%20today%20the%20telecom%20firms%20claimed%20a%20grave%20error%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Telecommunications%2C%20or%20DoT%2C%20in%20calculating%20those%20dues%20-%20licence%20fees%20and%20spectrum%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20indicate%20the%20DoT-calculated%20AGR%20dues%20total%20over%20Rs%201%20lakh%20crore%3B%20Airtel%20is%20believed%20to%20owe%20Rs%2043%2C980%20crore%20and%20Vodafone%20Rs%2058%2C254%20crore.%20But%20per%20the%20companies'%20own%20calculations%2C%20Airtel%20said%20it%20owed%20only%20Rs%2013%2C004%20crore%20and%20Vodafone%20claimed%20dues%20of%20only%20Rs%2021%2C533%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilar%20recalculations%20were%20made%20against%20dues%20owed%20by%20other%20companies%2C%20including%20Tata%20Teleservices.%20The%20telecom%20firms%20also%20complained%20about%20the%20court's%20%26quot%3Barbitrary%20penalty%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComputation%20of%20AGR%20is%20the%20basis%20for%20revenue-sharing%20between%20telecom%20firms%20and%20the%20government%2C%20which%20receives%20money%20for%20allotting%20licences%20and%20spectrum%20usage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DoT%20calculates%20the%20government's%20share%20as%20a%20percentage%20of%20the%20AGR.%20This%20amounts%20to%20three%20to%20five%20per%20cent%20in%20spectrum%20usage%20fees%20and%20eight%20per%20cent%20as%20licensing%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20exactly%20the%20AGR%20is%20calculated%20has%20been%20a%20contentious%20point%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades%20now%2C%20with%20the%20telecom%20firms%20insisting%20it%20must%20only%20include%20core%20revenue.%20The%20government%2C%20however%2C%20includes%20all%20revenue%2C%20including%20those%20from%20non-telecom%20channels%2C%20in%20its%20calculation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20government%2C%20and%20ordered%20the%20telecom%20firms%20to%20pay%20up%20Rs%2092%2C000%20crore%20within%20180%20days.%20That%20order%20hit%20the%20telecom%20industry%20hard%3B%20Vodafone%20India%20and%20Bharti%20Airtel%20posted%20record%20losses%20in%20the%20following%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202022%20Airtel%20said%20it%20had%20opted%20to%20defer%20payment%20of%20approximately%20Rs%203%2C000%20crore%20in%20AGR%20up%20to%20FY%202018%2F19%20-%20not%20tabulated%20in%20the%20court's%202019%20order%20-%20by%20four%20years.%20A%20week%20earlier%20Vodafone%20said%20it%20too%20had%20decided%20to%20defer%20payment%20of%20additional%20AGR%20dues%20of%20Rs.%208%2C837%20crore%20by%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20after%20the%20DoT%20raised%20an%20AGR%20demand%20for%20two%20financial%20years%20beyond%202016%2F17%2C%20which%20were%20not%20covered%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726727460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-02%2Fa1ooga8_supreme-court-of-india_650x400_14_February_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsetback-for-telecom-firms-in-supreme-court-plea-on-agr-rejected-6599567%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20rejected%20telecom%20companies'%20plea%20to%20re-compute%20adjusted%20gross%20revenues%2C%20or%20AGRs%2C%20amid%20a%20long-standing%20dispute%20over%20payment%20of%20dues%20to%20the%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%2