%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20weeks%20ago%2C%20Sahid%20S.K.%2C%20an%20AI%20artist%20and%20creator%20based%20in%20Arambag%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20teamed%20up%20with%20the%20Rajasthan%20police%20to%20help%20find%20missing%20children.%20Sahid%20is%20also%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Megalodon%2C%20a%20creative%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20cops%20from%20Rajasthan%20approached%20him%20about%20recreating%20the%20old%2C%20worn-out%20photos%20of%20the%20missing%20children%2C%20the%20opportunity%20to%20make%20AI%20work%20for%20people%20was%20clear.%20Using%20AI%20tools%2C%20the%20images%20of%20the%20kids%20could%20be%20recreated%2C%20imagining%20how%20they%20would%20look%20today%2C%20helping%20people%20identify%20them%20years%20after%20they%20went%20missing.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20given%20old%2C%20faded%20pictures%20where%20you%20could%20barely%20see%20the%20children's%20faces.%20I%20reconstructed%20their%20faces%20using%20AI%20tools%20and%20age-progression%20technology%20to%20estimate%20their%20current%20appearance.%20It%20was%20challenging%2C%20but%20knowing%20that%20this%20could%20help%20reunite%20families%20was%20all%20the%20motivation%20I%20needed%2C%26quot%3B%20Sahid%20said%20in%20a%20LinkedIn%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20hour%2C%20six%20children%20go%20missing%20in%20India.%20According%20to%20the%20National%20Crime%20Record%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%2C%20over%202%2C000%20girls%20go%20missing%20every%20day%20in%20the%20country.%20From%20around%2066%2C000%20missing%20girls%20in%202018%2C%20over%2085%2C000%20girls%20went%20missing%20in%20the%20year%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20these%20are%20just%20the%20reported%20numbers.%20Organisations%20working%20in%20the%20field%20estimate%20that%20millions%20go%20missing%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EChildren%20At%20Risk%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20travel%20primarily%20on%20trains%2C%20and%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20usual%20pictures%20of%20rivers%2C%20tracks%2C%20and%20hills%2C%20the%20most%20common%20imagery%20is%20children%20loitering%20around%20different%20platforms.%20According%20to%20Railway%20Children%20India%2C%20every%20five%20minutes%2C%20a%20child%20arrives%20alone%20at%20a%20railway%20platform%20in%20the%20country.%20These%20kids%20become%20the%20target%20of%20drug%20peddlers%2C%20traffickers%2C%20and%20other%20predators.%20Over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20Railway%20Children%20claims%20it%20has%20reunited%2022%2C740%20children%20with%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20sure%20the%20reunion%20stories%20are%20fulfilling%20and%20deeply%20moving.%20For%20each%20family%2C%20this%20reunion%20means%20the%20world.%20But%20I%20also%20wonder%20if%20AI%20can%20be%20leveraged%20even%20deeper%20and%20at%20a%20larger%20scale%20to%20create%20a%20more%20significant%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsn't%20that%20what%20a%20disruptive%20new%20technology%20is%20expected%20to%20do%20-%20change%20the%20game%20exponentially%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20Fighting%20Crime%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20in%20January%2C%20Delhi%20police%20used%20AI%20tools%20to%20not%20just%20identify%20a%20dead%20victim's%20body%20but%20also%20find%20his%20killer.%20As%20reported%20by%20%3Cem%3ENDTV's%20%3C%2Fem%3EMukesh%20Singh%20Sengar%2C%20on%20January%2010%2C%20the%20body%20of%20a%20young%20man%20was%20found%20near%20the%20Geeta%20Colony%20flyover%20in%20east%20Delhi.%20His%20face%20was%20beyond%20recognition%2C%20so%20the%20cops%20reconstructed%20his%20image%20using%20AI%20and%20printed%20over%20500%20posters%20circulated%20across%20the%20locality.%20A%20man%20came%20forward%2C%20recognising%20Hitendra%2C%20giving%20clues%20for%20further%20investigation%2C%20and%20finally%20nabbing%20the%20culprits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intersection%20of%20AI%20and%20crime%20is%20mostly%20scary.%20But%20in%20a%20very%20tiny%20way%2C%20it%20also%20promises%20to%20solve%20crimes%2C%20not%20just%20enable%20them.%20As%20I%20wrote%20earlier%20this%20year%20in%20my%20column%2C%20%3Cem%3EAI%20To%20Solve%20A%20Murder%20-%20Future%20Of%20Crime%20Fighting%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20sometimes%2C%20AI%20surprises%20us%20in%20good%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20are%20early%20examples%20of%20how%20simple%20AI%20tools%20can%20be%20used%20to%20find%20missing%20children%2C%20they%20are%20not%20enough%20to%20move%20the%20needle%20at%20a%20national%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20perhaps%20a%20great%20opportunity%20to%20train%20an%20AI%20model%20with%20all%20the%20missing%20children's%20data%20and%20make%20it%20work%20to%20solve%20the%20problem.%20In%20fact%2C%20there%20are%20examples%20from%20across%20the%20world%20of%20countries%20like%20the%20U.S.%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20Japan%20using%20AI%20at%20a%20national%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20Fast%20Company%20article%2C%20the%20National%20Center%20for%20Missing%20%26amp%3B%20Exploited%20Children%20(NCMEC)%20shared%20how%20they%20use%20AI%20to%20locate%20missing%20children%20faster.%20With%20over%2022%2C000%20cases%20of%20missing%20children%20reported%20yearly%20in%20the%20U.S.%2C%20the%20NCMEC%20now%20uses%20AI%20tools%20to%20streamline%20the%20investigation%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20tool%2C%20Logikcull%2C%20helps%20sift%20through%20mountains%20of%20documents%20and%20data%20to%20find%20crucial%20information%20for%20building%20legal%20cases%20against%20child%20abductors%20or%20abusers.%20This%20technology%20has%20already%20saved%20NCMEC%20more%20than%204%2C000%20hours%20of%20document%20review%2C%20freeing%20up%20their%20small%20legal%20and%20imaging%20teams%20to%20focus%20on%20reuniting%20families%20and%20helping%20children.%20As%20Gavin%20Portnoy%2C%20VP%20at%20NCMEC%2C%20highlights%2C%20AI%20tools%20allow%20the%20organisation%20to%20cut%20through%20the%20overwhelming%20volume%20of%20reports%20and%20use%20their%20limited%20resources%20more%20effectively%20to%20help%20those%20in%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20Fear%20To%20Hope%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20the%20paranoia%20around%20AI%20surveillance%2C%20job%20disruption%2C%20and%20warfare%20has%20hogged%20the%20headlines.%20For%20people%20and%20society%20at%20large%20to%20realise%20that%20AI%20can%20be%20both%20dark%20and%20illuminating%2C%20we%20need%20the%20most%20positive%20use%20cases.%20Solving%20India's%20missing%20children%20problem%20is%20clearly%20right%20up%20there%2C%20asking%20for%20the%20top%20AI%20researchers%20to%20shed%20their%20lab%20coats%20and%20jump%20right%20into%20solving%20this%20at%20a%20population%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20know%20of%20people%20and%20organisations%20with%20the%20tools%2C%20empathy%2C%20and%20heart%20to%20help%20India's%20missing%20children%20reunite%20with%20their%20families%2C%20please%20send%20me%20a%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Pankaj%20Mishra%20is%20the%20AI%20Editor%20at%20NDTV.%20He%20shapes%20stories%20and%20conversations%20that%20help%20explain%20AI%20in%20India%20and%20how%20it%20influences%20people's%20lives%20and%20work)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726726800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fj70bbaq8_ai_625x300_19_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcan-ai-help-find-indias-missing-children-6599641%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AI%20tools%20are%20reshaping%20the%20search%20for%20missing%20children%2C%20but%20is%20it%20enough%3F%20How%20do%20we%20scale%20this%20nationally%20to%20solve%20the%20crisis%20truly%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcan-ai-help-find-indias-missing-children-6599641%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Boeing%20says%20it's%20going%20to%20start%20furloughing%20'a%20large%20number'%20of%20its%20white-collar%20employees%20amid%20strike%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225584%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Boeing%20Employees%20Renton%20Washington%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66dfd13aa0ff598b26660769%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223409%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBoeing%20will%20temporarily%20furlough%20US-based%20employees%20following%20a%20strike.%3Cp%3EStephen%20Brashear%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBoeing%20is%20slated%20to%20furlough%20thousands%20of%20employees%20after%2030%2C000%20workers%20began%20a%20strike%20last%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20strike%20halted%20production%20of%20key%20planes%20like%20the%20737%20MAX.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBoeing's%20last%20strike%20in%202008%20caused%20significant%20revenue%20losses%2C%20highlighting%20the%20high%20stakes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Boeing%20announced%20it%20will%20be%20temporarily%20furloughing%20a%20%26quot%3Blarge%20number%26quot%3B%20of%20white-collar%20employees.%20The%20news%20comes%20after%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-workers-preparing-to-strike-rejected-contract-wage-increase-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E30%2C000%20Boeing%20workers%20began%20a%20strike%20on%20Friday%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20rejecting%20a%20new%20pay%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20initiating%20temporary%20furloughs%20over%20the%20coming%20days%20that%20will%20impact%20a%20large%20number%20of%20US-based%20executives%2C%20managers%2C%20and%20employees%2C%26quot%3B%20Kelly%20Ortberg%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Boeing%2C%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESelected%20employees%20will%20take%20one%20week%20of%20furlough%20every%20four%20weeks%20on%20a%20rolling%20basis%2C%20Ortberg%20wrote.%20Employees%20will%20find%20out%20the%20details%20of%20h