w%5C%22%3ESeptember%2019%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20responding%20to%20a%20post%20by%20BJP%20leader%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%2C%20who%20described%20Anna's%20death%20as%20%26quot%3Bvery%20sad%20but%20also%20disturbing%20at%20many%20levels%26quot%3B%20and%20sought%20a%20probe%20into%20her%20family's%20allegations%20of%20an%20exploitative%20work%20environment%20at%20Ernst%20and%20Young%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Heartbroken%20Mother's%20Letter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20Ernst%20%26amp%3B%20Young%20India%20chairman%20Rajiv%20Memani%2C%20Anna's%20mother%20Anita%20Augustine%20said%20her%20daughter%20died%20just%20four%20months%20after%20joining%20the%20company%20and%20called%20on%20its%20leadership%20to%20change%20a%20work%20culture%20that%20%26quot%3Bseems%20to%20glorify%20overwork%20while%20neglecting%20the%20very%20human%20being%20behind%20the%20role%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20writing%20this%20letter%20as%20a%20grieving%20mother%20who%20has%20lost%20her%20precious%20child%2C%20Anna%20Sebastian%20Perayil.%20My%20heart%20is%20heavy%2C%20and%20my%20soul%20is%20shattered%20as%20I%20pen%20these%20words%2C%20but%20I%20believe%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20share%20our%20story%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20no%20other%20family%20will%20have%20to%20endure%20the%20pain%20we%20are%20going%20through%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20mother%20wrote%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20wrote%20that%20Anna%20was%20an%20excellent%20student%20who%20topped%20through%20school%20and%20college%20and%20cleared%20the%20tough%20chartered%20accountancy%20exam%20with%20distinction.%20%26quot%3BEY%20was%20her%20first%20job%2C%20and%20she%20was%20thrilled%20to%20be%20part%20of%20such%20a%20prestigious%20company.%20But%20four%20months%20later%2C%20on%20July%2020th%2C%202024%2C%20my%20world%20collapsed%20when%20I%20received%20the%20devastating%20news%20that%20Anna%20had%20passed%20away.%20She%20was%20just%2026%20years%20old.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20heartbroken%20mother%20narrated%20the%20events%20weeks%20before%20she%20got%20the%20crushing%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20Saturday%2C%20July%206th%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20reached%20Pune%20to%20attend%20Anna's%20CA%20Convocation.%20Since%20she%20had%20been%20complaining%20of%20chest%20constriction%20upon%20reaching%20her%20PG%20late%20at%20night%20(around%201%20am)%20for%20the%20past%20week%2C%20we%20took%20her%20to%20the%20hospital%20in%20Pune.%20Her%20ECG%20was%20normal%2C%20and%20the%20cardiologist%20came%20to%20allay%20our%20fears%2C%20telling%20us%20she%20wasn't%20getting%20enough%20sleep%20and%20was%20eating%20very%20late.%20He%20prescribed%20antacids%2C%20which%20reassured%20us%20that%20it%20wasn't%20anything%20serious%20Though%20we%20had%20come%20all%20the%20way%20from%20Kochi%2C%20she%20insisted%20on%20going%20to%20work%20after%20seeing%20the%20doctor%2C%20saying%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20to%20be%20done%20and%20she%20wouldn't%20get%20leave.%20That%20night%2C%20she%20returned%20to%20her%20PG%20late%20again%20On%20Sunday%2C%20July%207th%2C%20the%20day%20of%20her%20convocation%2C%20she%20joined%20us%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20but%20she%20was%20working%20from%20home%20even%20that%20day%20until%20the%20afternoon%2C%20and%20we%20reached%20the%20convocation%20venue%20late%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20my%20daughter's%20great%20dream%20to%20take%20her%20parents%20to%20her%20convocation%20with%20her%20own%20hard-earned%20money.%20She%20booked%20our%20flight%20tickets%20and%20took%20us.%20It%20breaks%20my%20heart%20to%20tell%20you%20that%20even%20during%20those%20two%20days%2C%20which%20were%20the%20last%20we%20would%20spend%20with%20our%20child%2C%20she%20couldn't%20enjoy%20them%20because%20of%20the%20work%20pressure.%26quot%3B%C2%A0Anita%20Augustine%20wrote%20that%20Anna%20worked%20late%20into%20the%20night%2C%20even%20on%20weekends%2C%20%26quot%3Bwith%20no%20opportunity%20to%20catch%20her%20breath%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BHer%20assistant%20manager%20once%20called%20her%20at%20night%20with%20a%20task%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20completed%20by%20the%20next%20morning%2C%20leaving%20her%20with%20barely%20any%20time%20to%20rest%20or%20recover.%20When%20she%20voiced%20her%20concerns%2C%20she%20was%20met%20with%20the%20dismissive%20response%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20work%20at%20night%2C%20that's%20what%20we%20all%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnna%20would%20return%20to%20her%20room%20utterly%20exhausted%2C%20sometimes%20collapsing%20on%20the%20bed%20without%20even%20changing%20her%20clothes%2C%20only%20to%20be%20bombarded%20with%20messages%20asking%20for%20more%20reports.%20She%20was%20putting%20in%20her%20best%20efforts%2C%20working%20very%20hard%20to%20meet%20the%20deadlines.%20She%20was%20a%20fighter%20to%20the%20core%2C%20not%20someone%20to%20give%20up%20easily.%20We%20told%20her%20to%20quit%2C%20but%20she%20wanted%20to%20learn%20and%20gain%20new%20exposure.%20However%2C%20the%20overwhelming%20pressure%20proved%20too%20much%20even%20for%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20mother%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20said%20they%20were%20deeply%20hurt%20because%20no%20one%20from%20the%20organisation%20attended%20Anna's%20funeral.%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20from%20EY%20attended%20Anna's%20funeral.%20This%20absence%20at%20such%20a%20critical%20moment%2C%20for%20an%20employee%20who%20gave%20her%20all%20to%20your%20organization%20until%20her%20last%20breath%2C%20is%20deeply%20hurtful.%20Anna%20deserved%20better%2C%20and%20so%20do%20all%20the%20employees%20who%20continue%20to%20work%20under%20these%20conditions%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20mother%20wrote%2C%20hoping%20that%20her%20daughter's%20experience%20%26quot%3Bleads%20to%20real%20change%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Ernst%20%26amp%3B%20Young%20India%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EErnst%20%26amp%3B%20Young%20India%20has%20issued%20a%20statement%20and%20said%20it%20was%20deeply%20saddened%20by%20Anna's%20death%20and%20was%20taking%20the%20family's%20correspondence%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Butmost%20seriousness%20and%20humility%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20deeply%20saddened%20by%20Anna%20Sebastian's%20tragic%20and%20untimely%20passing%20in%20July%202024%2C%20and%20our%20deepest%20condolences%20go%20to%20the%20bereaved%20family.%20Anna%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Audit%20team%20at%20S%20R%20Batliboi%2C%20a%20member%20firm%20of%20EY%20Global%2C%20in%20Pune%20for%20a%20brief%20period%20of%20four%20months%2C%20joining%20the%20firm%20on%2018%20March%202024.%20That%20her%20promising%20career%20was%20cut%20short%20in%20this%20tragic%20manner%20is%20an%20irreparable%20loss%20for%20all%20of%20us.%20While%20no%20measure%20can%20compensate%20for%20the%20loss%20experienced%20by%20the%20family%2C%20we%20have%20provided%20all%20the%20assistance%20as%20we%20always%20do%20in%20such%20times%20of%20distress%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20taking%20the%20family's%20correspondence%20with%20the%20utmost%20seriousness%20and%20humility.%20We%20place%20the%20highest%20importance%20on%20the%20well-being%20of%20all%20employees%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20improve%20and%20provide%20a%20healthy%20workplace%20for%20our%201%2C00%2C000%20people%20across%20EY%20member%20firms%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726726680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F3ulfb94o_anna-sebastian_625x300_19_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanna-sebastian-perayil-ernst-young-centre-probes-26-year-old-ey-employees-death-as-mother-blames-overwork-6599624%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20massive%20outrage%20over%20the%20death%20of%20a%2026-year-old%20chartered%20accountant%20with%20Ern