m-india-enters-ukraine-raising-russian-ire%2Farticleshow%2F113480217.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ammunition%20From%20India%20Enters%20Ukraine%20Despite%20Russia's%20Reservations%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EArtillery%20shells%20sold%20by%20Indian%20arms%20makers%20have%20been%20diverted%20by%20European%20customers%20to%20Ukraine%20and%20New%20Delhi%20has%20not%20intervened%20to%20stop%20the%20trade%20despite%20protests%20from%20Moscow%2C%20according%20to%20eleven%20Indian%20and%20European%20government%20and%20defence%20industry%20officials%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20Reuters%20analysis%20of%20commercially%20available%20customs%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20transfer%20of%20munitions%20to%20support%20Ukraine's%20defence%20against%20Russia%20has%20occurred%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20sources%20and%20the%20customs%20data.%20Indian%20arms%20export%20regulations%20limit%20the%20use%20of%20weaponry%20to%20the%20declared%20purchaser%2C%20who%20risks%20future%20sales%20being%20terminated%20if%20unauthorised%20transfers%20occur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kremlin%20has%20raised%20the%20issue%20on%20at%20least%20two%20occasions%2C%20including%20during%20a%20July%20meeting%20between%20Russian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Sergei%20Lavrov%20and%20his%20Indian%20counterpart%2C%20three%20Indian%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetails%20of%20the%20ammunition%20transfers%20are%20reported%20by%20Reuters%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foreign%20and%20defence%20ministries%20of%20Russia%20and%20India%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20questions.%20In%20January%2C%20Indian%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20told%20a%20news%20conference%20that%20India%20had%20not%20sent%20or%20sold%20artillery%20shells%20to%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20Indian%20government%20and%20two%20defence%20industry%20sources%20told%20Reuters%20that%20Delhi%20produced%20only%20a%20very%20small%20amount%20of%20the%20ammunition%20being%20used%20by%20Ukraine%2C%20with%20one%20official%20estimating%20that%20it%20was%20under%201%25%20of%20the%20total%20arms%20imported%20by%20Kyiv%20since%20the%20war.%20The%20news%20agency%20couldn't%20determine%20if%20the%20munitions%20were%20resold%20or%20donated%20to%20Kyiv%20by%20the%20European%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20European%20countries%20sending%20Indian%20munitions%20to%20Ukraine%20are%20Italy%20and%20the%20Czech%20Republic%2C%20which%20is%20leading%20an%20initiative%20to%20supply%20Kyiv%20with%20artillery%20shells%20from%20outside%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Spanish%20and%20a%20senior%20Indian%20official%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20former%20top%20executive%20at%20Yantra%20India%2C%20a%20state-owned%20company%20whose%20munitions%20are%20being%20used%20by%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20official%20said%20that%20Delhi%20was%20monitoring%20the%20situation.%20But%2C%20along%20with%20a%20defence%20industry%20executive%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20the%20transfers%2C%20he%20said%20India%20had%20not%20taken%20any%20action%20to%20throttle%20the%20supply%20to%20Europe.%20Like%20most%20of%20the%2020%20people%20interviewed%20by%20Reuters%2C%20they%20spoke%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20due%20to%20the%20sensitivity%20of%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ukrainian%2C%20Italian%2C%20Spanish%20and%20Czech%20defence%20ministries%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20and%20Washington%2C%20Ukraine's%20main%20security%20backer%2C%20have%20recently%20strengthened%20defence%20and%20diplomatic%20cooperation%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20a%20rising%20China%2C%20which%20both%20regard%20as%20their%20main%20rival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20also%20has%20warm%20ties%20with%20Russia%2C%20its%20primary%20arms%20supplier%20for%20decades%2C%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20refused%20to%20join%20the%20Western-led%20sanctions%20regime%20against%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Delhi%2C%20long%20the%20world's%20largest%20weapons%20importer%2C%20also%20sees%20the%20lengthy%20war%20in%20Europe%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20develop%20its%20nascent%20arms%20export%20sector%2C%20according%20to%20six%20Indian%20sources%20familiar%20with%20official%20thinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkraine%2C%20which%20is%20battling%20to%20contain%20a%20Russian%20offensive%20toward%20the%20eastern%20logistics%20hub%20of%20Pokrovsk%2C%20has%20a%20dire%20shortage%20of%20artillery%20ammunition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20declined%20to%20comment%20and%20the%20U.S.%20State%20Department%20referred%20questions%20on%20Delhi's%20arms%20exports%20to%20the%20Indian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20exported%20just%20over%20%243%20billion%20of%20arms%20between%202018%20and%202023%2C%20according%20to%20data%20compiled%20by%20the%20Stockholm%20International%20Peace%20Research%20Institute%20think-tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%20at%20an%20Aug.%2030%20conference%20that%20defence%20exports%20surpassed%20%242.5%20billion%20in%20the%20last%20fiscal%20year%20and%20that%20Delhi%20wanted%20to%20increase%20that%20to%20about%20%246%20billion%20by%202029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommercially%20available%20customs%20records%20show%20that%20in%20the%20two%20years%20before%20the%20February%202022%20invasion%2C%20three%20major%20Indian%20ammunition%20makers%20-%20Yantra%2C%20Munitions%20India%20and%20Kalyani%20Strategic%20Systems%20-%20exported%20just%20%242.8%20million%20in%20munitions%20components%20to%20Italy%20and%20the%20Czech%20Republic%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Spain%20and%20Slovenia%2C%20where%20defence%20contractors%20have%20invested%20heavily%20in%20supply%20chains%20for%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%20February%202022%20and%20July%202024%2C%20the%20figure%20had%20increased%20to%20%24135.25%20million%2C%20the%20data%20show%2C%20including%20completed%20munitions%2C%20which%20India%20began%20exporting%20to%20the%20four%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArzan%20Tarapore%2C%20an%20India%20defence%20expert%20at%20Stanford%20University%2C%20said%20that%20Delhi's%20push%20to%20expand%20its%20arms%20exports%20was%20a%20major%20factor%20in%20the%20transfer%20of%20its%20arms%20to%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProbably%20in%20the%20sudden%20recent%20expansion%2C%20some%20instances%20of%20end-user%20violations%20have%20occurred.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDiscreet%20Deliveries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlisted%20Italian%20defence%20contractor%20Meccanica%20per%20l'Elettronica%20e%20Servomeccanismi%20(MES)%20was%20among%20the%20companies%20sending%20Indian-made%20shells%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20said%20the%20former%20top%20Yantra%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMES%20is%20Yantra's%20biggest%20foreign%20client.%20The%20executive%20said%20the%20Rome-based%20company%20buys%20empty%20shells%20from%20India%20and%20fills%20them%20with%20explosives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Western%20firms%20had%20explosive%20filling%20capabilities%20but%20lack%20the%20manufacturing%20capacity%20to%20mass%20produce%20artillery%20shells%2C%20the%20executive%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYantra%20said%20in%20its%202022-23%20annual%20report%20that%20it%20had%20agreed%20a%20deal%20with%20an%20unnamed%20Italian%20client%20to%20set%20up%20a%20manufacturing%20line%20for%20L15A1%20shells%2C%20which%20the%20former%20Yantra%20executive%20identified%20as%20MES.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMES%20and%20Yantra%20India%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20emails%20seeking%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECustoms%20data%20indicate%20that%20Yantra%20shipped%20%2435%20million%20worth%20of%20empty%20155mm%20L15A1%20shells%20to%20MES%20between%20February%202022%20and%20July%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECustoms%20records%20also%20show%20that%20in%20February%202024%2C%20U.K.-based%20arms%20company%20Dince%20Hill%20-%20whose%20board%20includes%20a%20top%20MES%20executive%20-%20exported%20%246.7%20million%20in%20ammunition%20from%20Italy%20to%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20exports%20were%20155mm%20L15A1%20shells%2C%20which%20the%20customs%20declaration%20said%20were%20manufactured%20by%20MES%20for%20Ukraine's%20Defence%20Ministry%20and%20supplied%20for%20%26quot%3Bpromoting%20the%20defense%20capability%20and%20mobilization%20readiness%20of%20Ukraine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDince%20Hill%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20an%20email%20seeking%20comment.%20Its%20new%20owner%2C%20Rome-based%20Effequattro%20Consulting%2C%20could%20not%20be%20reached.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20instance%2C%20Spain's%20Transport%20Minister%20Oscar%20Puente%20shared%20on%20social%20media%20in%20May%20an%20end%20user%20agreement%20signed%20by%20a%20Czech%20defence%20official%20that%20authorised%20the%20transfer%20of%20120mm%20and%20125mm%20ammunition%20shells%20from%20Munitions%20India%20to%20arms%20dealer%20Czech%20Defence%20Systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPro-Palestinian%20activists%20had%20alleged%20that%20the%20Borkum%2C%20a%20vessel%20carrying%20Indian-made%20arms%20which%20had%20stopped%20in%20a%20Spanish%20port%2C%20was%20carrying%20the%20weapons%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpanish%20newspaper%20El%20Mundo%20reported%20in%20May%20the%20final%20destination%20was%20actually%20Ukraine.%20A%20Spanish%20official%20and%20another%20source%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20confirmed%20to%20Reuters%20that%20Kyiv%20was%20the%20end%20user.%20Munitions%20India%20and%20CDS%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECustoms%20records%20dated%20March%2027%20show%20Munitions%20India%20had%20shipped%2010%2C000%20rounds%20of%20120mm%20and%20125mm%20mortar%20shells%2C%20worth%20more%20than%20%249%20million%2C%20from%20Chennai%20to%20CDS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFriendly%20Fire%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%2C%20which%20supplies%20more%20than%2060%25%20of%20Delhi's%20arms%20imports%2C%20is%20a%20valued%20partner%20for%20India.%20In%20July%2C%20PM%20Modi%20chose%20Moscow%20for%20his%20first%20bilateral%20international%20trip%20since%20being%20elected%20to%20a%20third%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20another%20meeting%20that%20month%20in%20Kazakhstan%20between%20top%20Indian%20diplomat%20Subrahmanyam%20Jaishankar%20and%20Lavrov%2C%20the%20Russian%20minister%20pressed%20his%20counterpart%20about%20Indian%20munitions%20being%20used%20by%20Ukrainians%20and%20complained%20that%20some%20were%20made%20by%20state-owned%20Indian%20companies%2C%20according%20to%20an%20Indian%20official%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20the%20encounter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20did%20not%20share%20Jaishankar's%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalter%20Ladwig%2C%20a%20South%20Asia%20security%20expert%20at%20King's%20College%20London%2C%20said%20the%20diversion%20of%20a%20relatively%20small%20amount%20of%20ammunition%20was%20geopolitically%20useful%20for%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20allows%20India%20to%20show%20partners%20in%20the%20West%20that%20it%20is%20not%20'on%20Russia's%20side'%20in%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Moscow%20held%20little%20leverage%20over%20Delhi's%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726726140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fp0gpcd_russiaukraine-war_625x300_14_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fammunition-from-india-enters-ukraine-despite-russias-reservations-report-6599581%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Artillery%20shells%20sold%20by%20Indian%20arms%20makers%20have%20been%20diverted%20by%20European%20customers%20to%20Ukraine%20and%20New%20Delhi%20has%20not%20intervened%20to%20stop%20the%20trade%20despite%20protests%20from%20Moscow