se%20firm%20Icom%20said%20Thursday%20that%20it%20had%20stopped%20producing%20the%20model%20of%20radios%20reportedly%20used%20in%20recent%20blasts%20in%20Lebanon%20around%2010%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20IC-V82%20is%20a%20handheld%20radio%20that%20was%20produced%20and%20exported%2C%20including%20to%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20from%202004%20to%20October%202014.%20It%20was%20discontinued%20about%2010%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20since%20then%2C%20it%20has%20not%20been%20shipped%20from%20our%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Icom%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20production%20of%20the%20batteries%20needed%20to%20operate%20the%20main%20unit%20has%20also%20been%20discontinued%2C%20and%20a%20hologram%20seal%20to%20distinguish%20counterfeit%20products%20was%20not%20attached%2C%20so%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20confirm%20whether%20the%20product%20shipped%20from%20our%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20products%20for%20overseas%20markets%20are%20sold%20exclusively%20through%20its%20authorized%20distributors%2C%20and%20that%20its%20export%20programme%20is%20based%20on%20Japanese%20security%20trade%20control%20regulations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20our%20radios%20are%20manufactured%20at%20our%20production%20subsidiary%2C%20Wakayama%20Icom%20Inc.%2C%20in%20Wakayama%20Prefecture%2C%20under%20a%20strict%20management%20system...%20so%20no%20parts%20other%20than%20those%20specified%20by%20our%20company%20are%20used%20in%20a%20product.%20In%20addition%2C%20all%20of%20our%20radios%20are%20manufactured%20at%20the%20same%20factory%2C%20and%20we%20do%20not%20manufacture%20them%20overseas%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20second%20wave%20of%20device%20explosions%20in%20as%20many%20days%2C%2020%20people%20died%20and%20more%20than%20450%20were%20wounded%20on%20Wednesday%20in%20Hezbollah%20strongholds%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5C