0in%20international%20cricket.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20Theories%20On%20How%20Israel%20May%20Have%20Triggered%20Hezbollah%20Device%20Blasts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwalkie-talkies-explode-in-hezbollahs-beirut-stronghold-day-after-pager-blasts-6595278%5C%22%3Epagers%20and%20walkie-talkies%3C%2Fa%3E%20used%20by%20Hezbollah%20members%20detonated%20across%20Lebanon%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20Wednesday%2C%20killing%20at%20least%2032%20people%20and%20injuring%20thousands%20more.%20This%20attack%20has%20sparked%20multiple%20theories%20about%20how%20these%20devices%20were%20sabotaged.%20While%20the%20exact%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2F%C2%A0https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpagers-then-walkie-talkies-how-devices-were-weaponised-against-hezbollah-6596167%5C%22%3Emechanism%20behind%20the%20explosions%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20still%20being%20investigated%2C%20a%20few%20theories%20have%20emerged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20debate%20centres%20around%20the%20idea%20that%20the%20pagers%20were%20tampered%20with%2C%20causing%20their%20batteries%20to%20overheat%20and%20explode.%20According%20to%20Lebanese%20Telecommunications%20Minister%20Johnny%20Corm%2C%20this%20overheating%20indicated%20%26quot%3Bfoul%20play%26quot%3B.%20However%2C%20cybersecurity%20expert%20Robert%20Graham%20quickly%20dismissed%20this%20theory%2C%20arguing%20that%20making%20batteries%20do%20more%20than%20burn%20is%20implausible.%20Instead%2C%20he%20suggested%20the%20far%20more%20likely%20explanation%20that%20someone%20bribed%20the%20factories%20involved%20to%20insert%20explosives%20into%20the%20devices%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happened%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20wave%20of%20explosions%20occurred%20on%20Tuesday%20when%20pagers%20used%20by%20the%20Iran-backed%20terror%20group%20detonated%20across%20Lebanon.%20Hospitals%20were%20quickly%20overwhelmed%20with%20casualties%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20field%20hospital%20in%20Tyre.%20These%20explosions%20came%20shortly%20after%20Israel%20announced%20a%20strategic%20expansion%20in%20its%20military%20actions%20against%20Hezbollah.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20a%20second%20wave%20of%20explosions%20involving%20Hezbollah%20walkie-talkies%20caused%20further%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETheory%201%3A%20Explosives%20planted%20in%20devices%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Lebanese%20security%20sources%20and%20reports%20by%20Reuters%2C%20a%20new%20batch%20of%205%2C000%20pagers%20ordered%20by%20Hezbollah%20from%20Taiwan-based%20manufacturer%20Gold%20Apollo%20had%20been%20compromised.%20Israeli%20spy%20intelligence%20agency%20Mossad%20is%20suspected%20of%20embedding%20small%20explosive%20devices%20within%20these%20devices.%20The%20explosives%2C%20reportedly%20as%20small%20as%203%20grams%2C%20were%20hidden%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20they%20went%20undetected%20by%20Hezbollah%20for%20months.%20The%20detonation%20mechanism%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20activated%20remotely%20via%20a%20coded%20message%20sent%20to%20the%20pagers.%20These%20explosives%2C%20experts%20say%2C%20were%20impossible%20to%20detect%20through%20regular%20scanners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20on%20the%20walkie-talkies%2C%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20purchased%20around%20the%20same%20time%2C%20has%20been%20linked%20to%20a%20similar%20sabotage%20operation.%20These%20devices%2C%20labelled%20as%20ICOM%20and%20reportedly%20made%20in%20Japan%2C%20are%20thought%20to%20have%20been%20tampered%20with%20at%20the%20production%20level%2C%20possibly%20by%20Mossad.%20The%20walkie-talkie%20explosions%20are%20less%20well-documented%2C%20but%20it%20is%20suggested%20that%20the%20same%20coded%20message%20method%20could%20have%20been%20used%20to%20activate%20the%20embedded%20explosives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETheory%202%3A%20Supply%20chain%20compromised%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20theory%20is%20the%20tampering%20of%20the%20supply%20chain.%20Security%20experts%20suggest%20that%20Israeli%20intelligence%20may%20have%20gained%20access%20to%20the%20devices%20long%20before%20they%20reached%20Hezbollah.%20The%20pagers%20were%20identified%20as%20Gold%20Apollo%20AR-924%20models%2C%20but%20further%20investigation%20revealed%20they%20were%20manufactured%20by%20BAC%20Consulting%20in%20Hungary%2C%20a%20company%20with%20licensing%20rights%20to%20use%20the%20Gold%20Apollo%20brand.%20This%20raises%20the%20possibility%20that%20the%20sabotage%20took%20place%20during%20the%20manufacturing%20or%20distribution%20stages%2C%20providing%20Israel%20an%20opportunity%20to%20install%20explosive%20materials%20without%20detection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20has%20since%20stated%20that%20the%20devices%20were%20part%20of%20a%20shipment%20recently%20imported%2C%20implying%20the%20tampering%20occurred%20before%20the%20pagers%20arrived%20in%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETheory%203%3A%20Remote%20activation%20via%20message%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20central%20theory%20is%20that%20the%20pagers%20and%20walkie-talkies%20were%20remotely%20detonated%20using%20an%20electronic%20signal%20or%20radio%20frequency%2C%20rather%20than%20physical%20tampering.%20Mark%20Montgomery%2C%20a%20retired%20admiral%20and%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Cyberspace%20Solarium%20Commission%2C%20suggested%20that%20the%20explosions%20may%20have%20been%20triggered%20by%20a%20radio%20frequency%20or%20electronic%20signal.%20%26quot%3BI%20suspect%20it%20was%20an%20intentional%20physical%20defect%20enabled%20by%20cyber%20or%20a%20radio%20frequency%20signal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20detonation%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20triggered%20by%20a%20coded%20message%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20from%20the%20New%20York%20Times.%20The%20pagers%20simultaneously%20received%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20an%20internal%20communication%20from%20Hezbollah%20leadership%2C%20which%2C%20upon%20opening%2C%20activated%20the%20explosives%20hidden%20within%20the%20devices.%20Videos%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%20supposedly%20show%20individuals%20looking%20at%20their%20pagers%20moments%20before%20the%20explosions%20occurred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20responsible%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20has%20blamed%20Israel%20for%20the%20attack%20and%20has%20vowed%20retaliation.%20The%20timing%20of%20the%20explosions%2C%20which%20followed%20Israel's%20announcement%20of%20extended%20military%20operations%20along%20the%20Lebanon%20border%2C%20has%20fuelled%20speculation%20that%20this%20was%20a%20deliberate%20move%20by%20Mossad.%20However%2C%20Israel%20has%20not%20commented%20on%20the%20matter%20officially.%20Further%20investigation%20is%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726724940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fqcrllkug_israel-hezbollah-attack-_625x300_18_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-did-hezbollah-pagers-walkie-talkies-explode-3-possible-explanations-6598964%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thousands%20of%20pagers%20and%20walkie-talkies%20used%20by%20Hezbollah%20members%20detonated%20across%20Lebanon%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20Wednesday%2C%20killing%20at%20least%2032%20people%20and%20injuring%20thousands%20more.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-did-hezbollah-pagers-walkie-talkies-explode-3-possible-explanations-6598964%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22YouTube%20announces%20Community%2C%20'Hyped'%20videos%2C%20and%20ads%20on%20paused%20screens%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22