Bcoward%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BEven%20his%20parents%20were%20insulted%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nadda%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20president%20accused%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20of%20resorting%20to%20politics%20of%20reservation%20and%20caste%20and%20inciting%20people%20against%20each%20other.%20%26quot%3BThen%20he%20goes%20abroad%20and%20talks%20about%20ending%20reservation%20and%20snatching%20away%20rights%20of%20people%20from%20Dalit%2C%20backward%20classes%20and%20tribal%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20gathering%20at%20a%20US%20university%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%20the%20Congress%20would%20think%20of%20scrapping%20reservations%20only%20when%20%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20a%20fair%20place%26quot%3B%2C%20which%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20not%20the%20case%20right%20now.%20The%20BJP%20latched%20on%20to%20the%20remark%20and%20said%20the%20Congress%20leader's%20prejudice%20against%20reservation%20is%20out%20in%20the%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nadda%20said%20it%20is%20the%20Congress%20that%20has%20insulted%20Indian%20democracy%20the%20most.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20imposed%20Emergency%2C%20backed%20triple%20talaq%2C%20defamed%20Constitutional%20institutions%20and%20weakened%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20Wrote%20To%20PM%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20in%20his%20letter%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20the%20Congress%20president%20had%20flagged%20a%20%26quot%3Bseries%20of%20objectionable%2C%20violent%20and%20indecent%26quot%3B%20remarks%20against%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EListing%20the%20verbal%20attacks%20on%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20pointed%20to%20Union%20Minister%20Ravneet%20Singh%20Bittu's%20%26quot%3BNumber%201%20terrorist%26quot%3B%20remark%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20announcing%20Rs%2011%20lakh%20for%20%26quot%3Banyone%20who%20cuts%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20tongue%20and%20Delhi%20BJP%20leader%20Tarwinder%20Singh%20Marwah's%20threat%20that%20Mr%20Gandhi%20will%20meet%20the%20same%20fate%20as%20his%20grandmother%20and%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndian%20culture%20is%20known%20across%20the%20world%20for%20non-violence%20and%20love...%20Gandhiji%20made%20these%20standards%20a%20key%20part%20of%20our%20politics%20during%20the%20British%20era.%20After%20Independence%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20long%20tradition%20of%20respectable%20disagreement%20between%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20the%20Opposition%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20chief%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20crores%20of%20Congress%20workers%20are%20worried%20over%20the%20BJP%20leaders'%20verbal%20attacks%20on%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20because%20of%20such%20forces%20spreading%20hate%20that%20Father%20of%20the%20Nation%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20had%20to%20sacrifice%20their%20lives.%20This%20political%20conduct%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20is%20the%20most%20indecent%20example%20in%20the%20history%20of%20democracy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20requested%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20enforce%20decorum%20and%20decency%20among%20BJP%20leaders.%20%26quot%3BThere%20should%20be%20strict%20legal%20action%20for%20such%20remarks%20so%20that%20Indian%20democracy%20can%20be%20saved%20from%20decline.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726723020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F4bjeun38_pm-modi-kharge-pti-650-_650x400_23_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarendra-modi-rahul-gandhi-mallikarjun-kharge-bjp-lists-abuses-against-pm-after-m-kharge-flags-barbs-at-rahul-gandhi-6599277%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20days%20after%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20wrote%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20flagging%20BJP%20leaders'%20objectionable%20remarks%20against%2