%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113477705.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESean%20%26quot%3BDiddy%26quot%3B%20Combs%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20Metropolitan%20Detention%20Center%20in%20Brooklyn%20after%20pleading%20not%20guilty%20to%20sex%20trafficking%20charges.%20The%20facility%20is%20known%20for%20its%20poor%20conditions%20and%20violence.%20His%20lawyers'%20request%20for%20house%20arrest%20was%20denied%2C%20highlighting%20ongoing%20concerns%20about%20the%20jail's%20safety%20and%20environment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-and-world%2Finside-the-brooklyn-federal-jail-where-sean-diddy-combs-is-locked-up-violence-squalor-and-death%2Farticleshow%2F113477705.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-and-world%2Finside-the-brooklyn-federal-jail-where-sean-diddy-combs-is-locked-up-violence-squalor-and-death%2Famp_articleshow%2F113477705.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-and-world%2Finside-the-brooklyn-federal-jail-where-sean-diddy-combs-is-locked-up-violence-squalor-and-death%2Famp_articleshow%2F113477705.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%3A%20Undoing%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20Legacy%20May%20Not%20Be%20Easy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.assettype.com%2Fbloombergquint%252F2019-04%252Fb566f9a9-fb8b-4209-b68b-e778716e0a56%252FPTI_Women_voters_show_their_fingers_marked_with_indelible_ink_after_casting_vote_at_Umpher_in_Ri_Bho.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%201967%2C%20independent%20India%20had%20witnessed%20four%20simultaneous%20elections%20for%20Parliament%20and%20state%20assemblies.%20The%20next%20national%20elections%20were%20scheduled%20for%201972%2C%20five%20years%20later.%20However%2C%20then-Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20had%20a%20different%20plan.%20A%20deep%20schism%20had%20developed%20between%20her%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bsyndicate%26quot%3B%20that%20had%20helped%20her%20become%20Prime%20Minister%20following%20the%20unfortunate%20death%20of%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri.%20She%20proved%20to%20be%20much%20shrewder%20than%20they%20had%20anticipated%2C%20shaking%20off%20the%20label%20of%20Goongi%20Gudia.%20The%20rift%20between%20her%20and%20her%20initial%20backers%20-%20the%20supposed%20stalwarts%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20-%20grew%20so%20significant%20that%20she%20was%20ultimately%20forced%20out%2C%20leading%20her%20to%20form%20a%20rival%20faction%2C%20Congress%20(R).%20She%20also%20initiated%20a%20coalition%20government%20with%20some%20non-Congress%20parties%2C%20marking%20India's%20first%20such%20experiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Fall%20Of%20The%20Coalition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20were%20challenging%20years%20for%20her.%20It%20soon%20became%20apparent%20that%20this%20coalition%20was%20unstable.%20In%20December%201970%2C%20Gandhi%20addressed%20the%20nation%2C%20announcing%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20about%2015%20months%20ahead%20of%20its%20term%20to%20call%20for%20a%20snap%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20simultaneous%20elections%20in%201967%2C%20the%20Congress%20party's%20nearly%20perfect%20winning%20streak%20was%20jolted%20when%20it%20lost%20five%20state%20assemblies%20and%20slipped%20to%20second%20place%20in%20four%20others.%20The%20next%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20held%20in%20early%201971%20instead%20of%20the%20scheduled%201972%2C%20decoupled%20parliamentary%20and%20state%20elections.%20By%20then%2C%20several%20state%20assemblies-such%20as%20those%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Nagaland%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20West%20Bengal-had%20experienced%20mid-term%20elections%20due%20to%20the%20fall%20of%20their%20respective%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Long-Pending%20Poll%20Promise%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20to%20September%2018%2C%202024%2C%20when%20the%20Union%20cabinet%2C%20chaired%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20approved%20his%20long-cherished%20idea%20of%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election.%20Modi%20has%20been%20advocating%20for%20this%20since%20he%20assumed%20office%20in%202014%2C%20and%20it%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20promises%20made%20by%20him%20and%20the%20BJP%20ahead%20of%20the%202019%20parliamentary%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20giving%20a%20Cabinet%20nod%20to%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%2C%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20took%20its%20first%20official%20step%20toward%20fulfilling%20one%20of%20its%20most%20significant%20electoral%20promises%2C%20coinciding%20with%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20first%20100%20days%20of%20Modi%20government%203.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETowards%20the%20end%20of%20its%20previous%20term%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20acted%20quickly%2C%20constituting%20a%20committee%20in%20September%202023%20headed%20by%20former%20President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind.%20This%20committee%20held%20extensive%20consultations%20with%20stakeholders%2C%20experts%2C%20and%20conducted%20research%2C%20ultimately%20submitting%20an%2018%2C626-page%20report%20to%20the%20President%20in%20March%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20widespread%20belief%20that%20implementing%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%20would%20necessitate%20a%20series%20of%20constitutional%20amendments%20and%20ratification%20by%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20state%20assemblies%2C%20the%20committee%20recommended%20that%20once%20Parliament%20passes%20the%20required%20amendments%2C%20state%20ratification%20would%20not%20be%20needed%20for%20simultaneous%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assembly%20polls.%20However%2C%20state%20ratification%20would%20be%20necessary%20once%20municipal%20and%20local%20body%20elections%20are%20aligned%20with%20national%20polls%2C%20which%20is%20proposed%20for%20a%20second%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Mechanism%20For%20ONOE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20will%20it%20work%3F%20According%20to%20the%20framework%20outlined%20by%20the%20committee%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20all%20state%20assemblies%20and%20local%20bodies%20will%20be%20dissolved%20as%20a%20one-time%20measure%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20remaining%20terms.%20This%20synchronization%20will%20allow%20parliamentary%20and%20state%20assembly%20polls%20to%20occur%20simultaneously%2C%20with%20local%20body%20elections%20held%20within%20100%20days%20thereafter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20event%20of%20a%20state%20government%20falling%20within%20the%20stipulated%20five%20years%2C%20where%20an%20alternative%20government%20cannot%20be%20formed%2C%20fresh%20elections%20for%20that%20hung%20assembly%20or%20local%20body%20would%20be%20conducted%20for%20the%20reduced%20term.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20such%20a%20scenario%20arises%20three%20years%20after%20the%20last%20election%2C%20a%20fresh%20election%20would%20occur%20for%20two%20years%2C%20ensuring%20alignment%20with%20the%20next%20national%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20also%20implies%20that%20a%20single%20electoral%20roll%20for%20parliamentary%2C%20state%2C%20and%20local%20body%20elections%20will%20need%20to%20be%20maintained%2C%20replacing%20the%20current%20system%20of%20three%20separate%20rolls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeavy%20Debate%20Expected%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%2047%20political%20parties%20that%20submitted%20their%20views%2C%2032%20supported%20simultaneous%20elections%20while%2015%20opposed%20them.%20In%20addition%20to%20soliciting%20public%20observations%2C%20the%20committee%20consulted%20legal%20experts-including%20four%20former%20Chief%20Justices%20of%20India%2C%20twelve%20former%20Chief%20Justices%20of%20major%20High%20Courts%2C%20four%20former%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioners%2C%20eight%20State%20Election%20Commissioners%2C%20and%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Law%20Commission%20of%20India.%20Business%20and%20industry%20bodies%20such%20as%20CII%2C%20FICCI%2C%20and%20ASSOCHAM%2C%20as%20well%20as%20prominent%20economists%2C%20were%20also%20consulted%20regarding%20the%20economic%20implications%20of%20holding%20simultaneous%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20draft%20constitutional%20amendment%20bill%20may%20be%20presented%20in%20Parliament%20during%20the%20winter%20session.%20If%20Parliament%20functions%20normally%2C%20the%20upcoming%20discussions%20on%20the%20constitutional%20amendment%20bills%20for%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20among%20the%20liveliest%20debates%20ever%20witnessed.%20However%2C%20executing%20this%20task%20will%20be%20easier%20said%20than%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Sanjay%20Singh%20is%20Contributing%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726720440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.assettype.com%2Fbloombergquint%252F2019-04%252Fb566f9a9-fb8b-4209-b68b-e778716e0a56%252FPTI_Women_voters_show_their_fingers_marked_with_indelible_ink_after_casting_vote_at_Umpher_in_Ri_Bho.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fone-nation-one-election-undoing-indira-gandhis-legacy-may-not-be-easy-6598980%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22By%20giving%20a%20Cabinet%20nod%20to%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%2C%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20took%20its%20first%20official%20step%20toward%20fulfilling%20one%20of%20its%20most%20significant%20electoral%20promises.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion