ting%20the%20Lebanese%20Health%20Ministry.%20The%20pagers%20exploded%20in%20Lebanon%20around%20Tuesday%20late%20afternoon.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20a%20more%20limited%20attack%20involving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmore-devices-explode-in-lebanon-after-deadly-hezbollah-pager-blasts-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewalkie-talkies%20and%20solar%20equipment%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20exploded%20injured%20hundreds%20more%20and%20killed%20at%20least%2020%20people%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Flebanon-israel-exploding-pagers-hezbollah-syria-ce6af3c2e6de0a0dddfae48634278288%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAP%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20cited%20the%20Lebanese%20Health%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20not%20commented%20or%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20attack.%20US%20and%20other%20officials%20who%20were%20briefed%20on%20the%20operation%20and%20who%20spoke%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20told%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F09%2F17%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Fisrael-hezbollah-pagers-explosives.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20Israel%20was%20behind%20the%20attack%20and%20infiltrated%20a%20batch%20of%20Taiwanese-branded%20pagers%20in%20order%20to%20plant%20explosives%20inside%20the%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpokespeople%20for%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20and%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Defense%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20attack%20of%20this%20size%20requires%20a%20massive%20amount%20of%20technical%20capabilities%20involving%20intelligence%20gathering%20and%20months%20of%20planning%2C%20a%20national%20security%20expert%20and%20arms%20expert%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20scale%20of%20this%20operation%20suggests%20a%20complex%20supply-chain%20attack%20exe