href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eonline.com%2Fnews%2F1407155%2Fbachelorettes-devin-strader-says-he-f-ked-up-after-sharing-messages-from-ex-jenn-tran%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EE!%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20then%20deleted%20and%20reuploaded%20the%20video%20with%20redacted%20messages.%20However%2C%20that%20video%20has%20also%20been%20deleted%20from%20his%20Instagram%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDevin%20then%20reportedly%20shared%20a%20since-deleted%20Instagram%20Story%20apologizing%20for%20sharing%20sensitive%20messages%20and%20asking%20for%20forgiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20deeply%20am%20so%20sorry%20for%20showing%20sensitive%20information%20from%20the%20bottom%20of%20my%20heart%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20reportedly%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThat%20was%20not%20my%20intention.%20My%20only%20intention%20is%20to%20show%20the%20relationship%20from%20my%20perspective.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20gain%20nothing%20from%20that%20text%20conversation%20being%20shown.%20I%20promise%20you%20that%20was%20a%20mistake%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20honestly%20missed%20this%20one%20and%20fucked%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESeptember%2012%2C%202024%3A%20Jenn%20says%20she%20feels%20%26quot%3Bbetrayed%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdisrespected%26quot%3B%20by%20Devin%20for%20posting%20their%20texts.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221922%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Devin%20Strader%20and%20Jenn%20Tran%20in%20a%20behind-the-scenes%20photo%20from%20season%2021%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelorette.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ea026dcfb7f307e5728aaf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221441%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDevin%20and%20Jenn%20in%20a%20behind-the-scenes%20photo%20from%20season%2021%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bachelorette.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EJohn%20Fleenor%2FDisney%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJenn%20returned%20to%20%26quot%3BThe%20Viall%20Files%26quot%3B%20to