ore%20thorough%20cleaning%2C%20you%20can%20easily%20run%20the%20cover%20and%20liner%20through%20the%20washer%20and%20dryer.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20somewhat%20difficult%20to%20weave%20the%20bolsters%20back%20into%20the%20cover.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cc39ffd0-3231-4b4c-a135-891a258ecb71%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20budget%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBest%20budget%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Brindle%20Waterproof%20Memory%20Foam%20Pet%20Bed%20evenly%20supported%20and%20conformed%20to%20our%20tester%20dog%2C%20a%2015-year-old%20Australian%20shepherd%20with%20multiple%20joint%20and%20mobility%20issues.%20The%204-inch-thick%20mattress%20proved%20resilient%2C%20too%2C%20showing%20no%20signs%20of%20flattening.%20It%20consists%20of%20two%20layers%3A%202%20inches%20of%20memory%20foam%20on%20top%20and%20a%202-inch%20bottom%20layer%20of%20dense%20support%20foam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20a%20textured%20velour%20surface%20and%20nonskid%20base%2C%20we%20felt%20at%20ease%20giving%20it%20to%20the%2050-pound%20Aussie%20prone%20to%20stumbling%20and%20sliding.%20While%20the%20lack%20of%20bolsters%20is%20ideal%20for%20dogs%20who%20like%20to%20sprawl%2C%20you'll%20do%20better%20with%20our%20budget%20bolster%20pick%20below%20if%20your%20dog%20likes%20to%20snuggle%20up%20against%20the%20sides%20of%20their%20bed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20small%20dogs%20are%20lying%20on%20the%20Brindle%20memory%20foam%20dog%20bed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eb3971ce3009a0fac771ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrindle%20makes%20one%20of%20the%20best%20orthopedic%20dog%20beds%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20real%20bargain%3Cp%3EAlex%20Rennie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20protective%20waterproof%20liner%20can't%20be%20removed%20for%20cleaning.%20However%2C%20it%20did%20its%20job%20well%2C%20keeping%20the%20foam%20interior%20completely%20dry%20in%20our%20waterproofing%20tests%20(we%20cut%20it%20open%20to%20check).%20With%20this%20bed's%20lower%20price%2C%20it's%20unsurprising%20that%20the%20cover%20is%20less%20durable%20than%20those%20found%20on%20more%20expensive%20beds.%20We%20tested%20two%20different%20sizes%2C%20and%20the%20cover%20on%20the%20small%20bed%20fit%20loosely%20and%20snagged%20during%20our%20digging%20test.%20However%2C%20our%20large%20bed%20tester%20found%20their%20cover%20very%20durable.%20Both%20covers%20came%20completely%20clean%20in%20the%20washing%20machine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229dc55c82-94cf-4dea-9083-09de57f273f1%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20budget%20with%20bolster%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBest%20budget%20with%20bolster%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20affordability%2C%20along%20with%20many%20size%20and%20color%20options%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20beat%20the%20Bedsure%20Orthopedic%20Dog%20Bed%2C%20which%20ranges%20in%20price%20from%20%2437%20to%20%24110%20depending%20on%20size.%20It%20impressed%20all%20of%20our%20human%20testers%20so%20much%20that%20we%20named%20it%20the%20top%20budget%20pick%20in%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-bed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebest%20dog%20beds%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bed%20has%20a%204-inch%20egg-crate%20foam%20mattress%20that%20offers%20medium-firm%20support%2C%20and%20the%20extra-large%20size%20didn't%20sink%20or%20sag%20under%20the%20weight%20of%20a%2070-pound%20English%20cream%20retriever.%20Her%20guardian%20moved%20it%20to%20wherever%20they%20were%20spending%20time%2C%20and%20she%20slept%20on%20it%20for%20hours%20at%20a%20time%2C%20indoors%20and%20out.%20Though%20not%20lightweight%2C%20the%20bed%20was%20reasonably%20easy%20to%20transport%20because%20its%20proportions%20were%20not%20too%20wide%20or%20awkward.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20golden%20lab%20is%20lying%20on%20a%20gray%20Bedsure%20dog%20bed%20on%20a%20dock%20beside%20the%20water.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eaf9eccfb7f307e572aa05%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAll%20of%20our%20testers%20approved%20of%20this%20budget-friendly%20bolster%20bed%20from%20Bedsure.%3Cp%3EAmy%20Graves%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20cover%20proved%20durable%2C%20and%20the%20waterproof%20liner%20protected%20the%20foam%20in%20our%20soaking%20test.%20Spot-cleaning%20the%20cover%20after%20we%20smeared%20it%20with%20dirt%20and%20peanut%20butter%20yielded%20mixed%20results.%20We%20tested%20this%20bed%20in%20two%20different%20colors%2C%20and%20the%20cream%20top%20of%20the%20caramel%20bed%20held%20onto%20some%20dirt.%20Although%20this%20stain%20came%20out%20in%20the%20washer%2C%20putting%20the%20bed%20in%20the%20machine%20was%20another%20issue.%20You%20can't%20remove%20the%20bolsters%20so%20you're%20left%20with%20a%20wet%20bulk%2C%20which%20may%20take%20longer%20to%20dry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20liner's%20zipper%20also%20failed.%20On%20one%20cover%2C%20it%20got%20stuck%20with%20repeated%20use%2C%20and%20on%20the%20other%2C%20it%20fell%20off%20after%20two%20rounds%20in%20the%20washing%20machine.%20However%2C%20given%20the%20bed's%20overall%20durability%2C%20we%20still%20recommend%20it%20and%20advise%20gentle%20handling%20of%20the%20zipper%20and%20handwashing%20the%20liner.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b3db0662-8570-4f9f-89be-df69088b820c%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20small%20dogs%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBest%20for%20small%20dogs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20a%20bolster%20on%20one%20end%20and%20a%20soft%20microsuede%20cover%2C%20the%20Big%20Barker%20Junior%20resembles%20a%20chaise%20lounge%2C%20though%20one%20designed%20exclusively%20for%20dogs%20under%2050%20pounds.%20We%20tested%20the%20medium%20size%20bed%20with%20a%2010-pound%20chihuahua%20mix%20and%20a%2012-pound%20terrier%20mix%2C%20and%20its%20firm%20core%20flawlessly%20supported%20their%20weight.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20small%20chihuahua%20mix%20is%20lying%20on%20the%20gray%20Big%20Barker%20Junior%20dog%20bed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eb3e57cfb7f307e572eb12%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBig%20Barker%20is%20well-regarded%20for%20its%20extra-large%20dog%20beds%2C%20and%20its%20small%20beds%20don't%20disappoint%20either.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Rennie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20foam%20was%20resilient%2C%20too%2C%20bouncing%20back%20immediately%20after%20our%20tester%20removed%20heavy%20weights%20to%20test%20for%20flattening.%20So%20long%20as%20your%20small%20dog%20does%20not%20have%20a%20problem%20climbing%20onto%20a%20surface%204%20inches%20off%20the%20floor%2C%20it's%20a%20great%20choice.%20The%20cover%20had%20no%20trouble%20standing%20up%20to%20the%20scratching%2C%20digging%2C%20and%20seam-strength%20tests%2C%20staying%20as%20good%20as%20new.%20%26quot%3BThis%20thing%20is%20durable%20with%20a%20capital%20D%2C''%20says%20our%20tester.%20Peanut%20butter%2C%20dirt%2C%20and%20black%20tea%20were%20easy%20to%20remove%20with%20spot-cleaning%20with%20dish%20soap%20and%20water.%20However%2C%20with%20only%20machine%20washing%2C%20peanut%20butter%20left%20oil%20stains%20on%20the%20cover.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20an%20expensive%20bed%20(just%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbigbarker.com%2Fproducts%2Fwaterproof-dog-bed-liner-barker-junior%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewaterproof%20liner%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20itself%20starts%20at%20%2450%20for%20the%20size%20small)%2C%20it%20should%20last%20a%20lifetime.%20Big%20Barker%20even%20offers%20a%2010-year%20guarantee%20because%20it%20is%20confident%20that%20the%20foam%20will%20retain%2090%25%20of%20its%20original%20shape%20and%20thickness%20for%20that%20long.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a5f0375d-bedb-4691-8f5f-431c647b209a%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20crates%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBest%20for%20crates%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Big%20Barker%204%26quot%3B%20Orthopedic%20Crate%20Bed%20is%20far%20more%20durable%20and%20supportive%20than%20a%20typical%20crate%20pad%2C%20making%20it%20a%20great%20choice%20for%20any%20dog%20who%20rests%20a%20long%20while%20in%20their%20crate.%20A%2050-pound%20basset-beagle%20mix%20was%20well%20supported%2C%20and%20their%20guardian%20also%20lay%20on%20the%20pad%20and%20couldn't%20feel%20the%20floor%20underneath.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bed%20has%20a%20tough%20microsuede%20cover%20with%20well-constructed%20seams%20and%20zippers%20that%20aced%20all%20durability%20tests.%20In%20testing%2C%20the%20two-layer%20foam%20core%20never%20flattened%20and%20filled%20back%20out%20in%20less%20than%20a%20minute%20after%20we%20removed%20dumbbell%20weights%20that%20had%20been%20laid%20on%20it%20for%20four%20hours.%20The%20cover%20acquired%20a%20%26quot%3Bdusty%26quot%3B%20look%20after%20washing%2C%20drying%2C%20and%20regular%20use%2C%20which%20is%20common%20with%20microfiber.%20We%20discovered%20the%20cover%20shrunk%20slightly%20after%20washing%20and%20drying%2C%20but%20we%20were%20able%20to%20reassemble%20it%20with%20a%20little%20extra%20effort.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bed's%20price%20and%20height%20may%20be%20deal-breakers%20for%20some.%20You'll%20also%20need%20to%20purchase%20the%20waterproof%20liner%20separately.%20The%204-inch%20thick%20foam%20could%20take%20away%20too%20much%20headroom%20from%20taller%20dogs%20unless%20their%20crate%20is%20very%20tall%2C%20while%20shorter%20dogs%20with%20limited%20mobility%20may%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20step%20in%20and%20out%20of%20their%20crate.%20Like%20the%20brand's%20Barker%20Junior%20bed%2C%20which%20we%20recommend%20for%20small%20dogs%2C%20this%20crate%20pad%20carries%20an%20unbeatable%2010-year%20guarantee.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2201232f66-2ccf-405d-849b-783047cb9cdb%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20an%20orthopedic%20dog%20bed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20our%20experts%2C%20there%20are%20some%20key%20features%20to%20look%20for%20when%20choosing%20a%20supportive%20orthopedic%20bed%20for%20your%20dog.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EMaterials%20and%20support%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EBrands%20can%20market%20their%20beds%20however%20they%20want%2C%20and%20not%20all%20foam%20mattresses%20are%20equal.%20However%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vet.cornell.edu%2Fresearch%2Ffaculty%2Fjoseph-j-wakshlag-dvm-phd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDr.%20Joseph%20J.%20Wakshlag%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20veterinarian%20and%20professor%20of%20clinical%20nutrition%20and%20sports%20medicine%20and%20rehabilitation%20at%20Cornell%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20Medicine%2C%20says%20that%20what%20works%20for%20humans%20at%20rest%20has%20been%20shown%20anecdotally%20to%20work%20for%20dogs%2C%20too.%20%26quot%3BThe%20memory%20foam%20approach%2C%20which%20is%20used%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20human%20beds%2C%20has%20made%20it%20to%20the%20dog%20arena%2C%20whereby%20they%20show%20that%20the%20pressure%20is%20more%20evenly%20distributed%20over%20a%20larger%20area%2C%20so%20there's%20less%20risk%20of%20sores%20and%20it's%20more%20comfortable%20for%20the%20dog%20in%20general%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20best%20orthopedic%20dog%20beds%20in%20this%20guide%20contain%20either%20polyurethane%20memory%20foam%20or%20what%20a%20brand%20may%20describe%20as%20orthopedic%20foam.%20If%20a%20bed%20contains%20lower-quality%20foam%2C%20it%20will%20break%20down%20faster%20and%20may%20feel%20flimsy%20or%20springy.%20In%20addition%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20look%20for%20beds%20that%20contain%20at%20least%202%20inches%20of%20foam.%20We've%20found%20anything%20less%20is%20not%20sufficient%20to%20offer%20orthopedic%20support%20for%20a%20dog%20of%20any%20size.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EComfort%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20bolstered%20or%20flat%20beds%20are%20suitable%20options%2C%20but%20it's%20important%20to%20choose%20the%20design%20that%20complements%20your%20dog's%20sleeping%20style.%20Meredith%20O'Connor%2C%20a%20dog%20behaviorist%20and%20trainer%2C%20says%20dogs%20sort%20out%20to%20be%20side%20sleepers%20or%20flat-out%20stretchers%20on%20a%20dog-by-dog%20basis.%20If%20your%20dog%20is%20a%20side%20sleeper%20who%20likes%20to%20lean%20against%20something%20while%20they%20sleep%20or%20prop%20their%20head%20up%20while%20lying%20down%2C%20a%20bolster%20bed%20is%20your%20best%20bet.%20Flat%20beds%20are%20excellent%20options%20for%20dogs%20who%20sleep%20sprawled%20out%20with%20their%20head%20even%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20their%20body.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EEase%20of%20entry%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EConditions%20such%20as%20arthritis%20and%20mobility%20challenges%20can%20make%20it%20difficult%20for%20dogs%20to%20get%20in%20and%20out%20of%20bed%2C%20but%20certain%20features%20can%20help%20ease%20your%20dog%20down%20to%20rest%20safely.%20Look%20for%20nonskid%20bottoms%2C%20reasonably%20thick%20pads%20that%20aren't%20too%20high%20to%20step%20onto%2C%20and%20wide%20spaces%20between%20bolsters%20so%20your%20dog%20won't%20encounter%20any%20obstacles%20climbing%20in%20and%20out%20of%20bed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EDurability%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20best%20orthopedic%20dog%20beds%20can%20set%20you%20back%20some%20change%2C%20so%20a%20bed%20that%20flattens%2C%20gets%20worn%20looking%20from%20rounds%20in%20the%20washing%20machine%2C%20or%20is%20easily%20ripped%20or%20scratched%20open%20will%20not%20pass%20muster.%20Consider%20beds%20with%20a%20dense%20memory%20foam%20core%20protected%20by%20either%20a%20waterproof%20cover%20or%20liner.%20Covers%20made%20of%20polyester%20and%20cotton%20both%20held%20up%20well%20in%20our%20testing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EWater%20resistance%20and%20ease%20of%20cleaning%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20some%20senior%20dogs%20and%20those%20recovering%20from%20surgery%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20have%20accidents%20and%20other%20hygiene%20issues%2C%20we%20recommend%20purchasing%20a%20waterproof%20bed%20with%20a%20cover%20that%20is%20easy%20to%20spot%20clean%20and%20comes%20completely%20clean%20after%20a%20stint%20in%20the%20washer%20and%20dryer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3ESizing%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20ensure%20your%20dog%20has%20room%20to%20stretch%20out%2C%20choose%20a%20sleeping%20surface%20slightly%20larger%20than%20their%20length%20measured%20from%20the%20nose%20to%20the%20base%20of%20the%20tail.%20Dogs%20with%20longer%20legs%20will%20also%20need%20a%20deep%20enough%20bed%20to%20accommodate%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EReturn%20policies%20and%20warranties%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20recommend%20beds%20with%20at%20least%20a%2030-day%20return%20policy%2C%20but%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20some%20refunds%20only%20apply%20to%20unused%20beds.%20The%20pricier%20the%20bed%2C%20the%20more%20likely%20you'll%20see%20a%20manufacturer%20warranty%20for%20defects.%20Before%20you%20buy%2C%20make%20sure%20to%20read%20the%20company's%20return%2C%20exchange%2C%20and%20warranty%20policies%20closely.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3ECertifications%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EMaterials%20safety%20certifications%20ensure%20that%20some%20or%20all%20of%20the%20materials%20in%20a%20product%20are%20free%20of%20materials%20known%20to%20be%20harmful%20to%20people.%20Products%20with%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcertipur.us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECertiPUR-US%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20certification%20contain%20polyurethane%20foam%20that%20is%20made%20without%20formaldehyde%2C%20ozone%20depleters%2C%20prohibited%20phthalates%2C%20mercury%2C%20lead%2C%20and%20other%20heavy%20metals.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20foam%20has%20low%20volatile%20organic%20compounds%20(VOCs)%20emissions%20and%20is%20not%20treated%20with%20flame%20retardants%2C%20which%20contain%20carcinogens%20and%20other%20toxins.%20A%20polyurethane%20foam%20producer%20needs%20to%20meet%20the%20criteria%20set%20by%20the%20Alliance%20for%20Flexible%20Polyurethane%20Foam%20to%20receive%20certification.%20The%20certification%20process%20includes%20submitting%20test%20results%20and%20samples%20along%20with%20a%20fee%20of%20several%20thousand%20dollars.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oeko-tex.com%2Fen%2Four-standards%2Foeko-tex-standard-100%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOEKO-TEX%20STANDARD%20100%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20certification%20is%20given%20after%20a%20manufacturer%20submits%20to%20an%20application%20process%20that%20includes%20a%20fee.%20OEKO-TEX%20STANDARD%20100%20signifies%20that%20every%20part%20of%20a%20product%20is%20free%20of%20various%20substances%20that%20may%20harm%20human%20health.%20To%20receive%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ul.com%2Fservices%2Ful-greenguard-certification%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGreenguard%20Gold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20certification%2C%20a%20manufacturer%20submits%20samples%20for%20laboratory%20testing%20to%20verify%20that%20they%20meet%20low%20chemical%20emissions%20standards%20set%20by%20UL%20Solutions%2C%20an%20international%20materials%20safety%20organization.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2231116957-c9b4-4126-8092-00ec01c66f24%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20orthopedic%20dog%20beds%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20select%20the%20best%20orthopedic%20dog%20beds%2C%20we%20tested%2012%20different%20designs%20with%20dogs%20of%20various%20breeds%20and%20weights%2C%20from%20ages%206%20to%2015%20and%2012%20to%20180%20pounds.%20Our%20tests%20evaluated%20comfort%2C%20support%2C%20durability%2C%20and%20ease%20of%20care.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EComfort%20and%20support%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3ELooking%20for%20the%20best%20options%20in%20each%20design%2C%20we%20looked%20for%20signs%20that%20our%20tester%20dogs%20were%20resting%20comfortably%20over%20the%20course%20of%20several%20weeks.%20We%20observed%20how%20much%20time%20they%20spent%20on%20the%20beds%20and%20whether%20they%20appeared%20fully%20relaxed%20while%20resting%20or%20sleeping.%20We%20got%20on%20the%20beds%20ourselves%20to%20assess%20how%20much%20support%20and%20stability%20the%20foam%20gave%20us%2C%20especially%20for%20our%20lower%20backs.%20Lastly%2C%20we%20used%20barbells%20and%20loaded%20duffle%20bags%20to%20see%20if%20any%20beds%20failed%20to%20support%20or%20spring%20back%20into%20their%20original%20shape%20after%20taking%20on%20the%20load.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERegardless%20of%20the%20foam%20type%2C%20we%20evaluated%20each%20bed%20to%20ensure%20it%20conformed%20to%20our%20tester%20dogs'%20bodies%20to%20distribute%20pressure%20evenly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EEase%20of%20entry%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20assessed%20how%20easily%20dogs%20could%20enter%20and%20settle%20into%20the%20beds.%20While%20extra-high%20beds%20can%20work%20for%20taller%20dogs%20and%20may%20provide%20better%20support%2C%20the%20best%20orthopedic%20dog%20beds%20tended%20to%20be%20somewhat%20lower-profile%20beds%20that%20were%20still%20firm%20and%20supportive.%20If%20a%20bed%20had%20a%20bolster%2C%20we%20made%20sure%20the%20entry%20points%20were%20wide%20enough%20for%20dogs%20to%20get%20in%20and%20out%20with%20ease.%20We%20also%20gave%20higher%20ratings%20to%20beds%20with%20nonskid%20bottoms%20and%20cover%20materials%20that%20weren't%20slippery%20to%20help%20pets%20avoid%20any%20sliding%20or%20scooting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EDurability%20and%20ease%20of%20cleaning%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20yanking%20on%20zippers%2C%20digging%20on%20covers%20with%20metal%20dinner%20forks%2C%20puncturing%20seams%20with%20scissors%2C%20and%20scraping%20bottoms%20with%20sandpaper%2C%20we%20looked%20for%20hard-nosed%20durability%20in%20these%20beds.%20We%20smeared%20the%20covers%20with%20dirt%20and%20peanut%20butter%20and%20poured%20black%20tea%20on%20them%2C%20to%20see%20which%20beds%20were%20easy%20to%20spot%20clean.%20Then%2C%20after%20machine-washing%20and%20drying%20the%20covers%20and%20liners%2C%20we%20reassembled%20everything%20and%20looked%20for%20any%20lingering%20spots%2C%20stains%2C%20or%20fabric%20changes.%20We%20gave%20the%20highest%20marks%20to%20beds%20that%20stayed%20both%20firm%20and%20plush%20over%20the%20course%20of%20many%20weeks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EWaterproofing%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20beds%20we%20selected%20claimed%20to%20have%20waterproof%20or%20water-resistant%20liners%2C%20and%20we%20made%20sure%20to%20test%20this%20ourselves.%20After%20pouring%20a%20cup%20of%20warm%20water%20onto%20the%20sleep%20surface%20of%20each%20bed%2C%20we%20waited%2030%20minutes%20before%20checking%20to%20see%20if%20any%20moisture%20made%20it%20through%20the%20liners%20to%20the%20foam%20mattress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2232480d9f-b058-4281-8ba6-fbd149e7081e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EOrthopedic%20dog%20beds%20FAQs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20orthopedic%20beds%20worth%20it%20for%20dogs%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDogs%20of%20any%20age%20can%20benefit%20from%20resting%20on%20an%20orthopedic%20dog%20bed%20made%20of%20memory%20foam%2C%20which%20distributes%20pressure%20over%20a%20large%20area.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20rather%20simple%20concept%20regarding%20pressure%20points%2C''%20Wakshlag%20says.%20%26quot%3BDepending%20on%20how%20the%20dog%20is%20lying%2C%20it%20creates%20pressure%20over%20areas%20like%20hips%20and%20elbows.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20addition%2C%20a%20restful%20stint%20on%20a%20bed%20with%20firm%20support%20is%20not%20just%20about%20the%20dog's%20comfort%20but%20also%20mobility%2C%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20extend%20longevity%20and%20can%20also%20help%20with%20behavior%20issues%2C%20says%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vet.cornell.edu%2Fresearch%2Ffaculty%2Fkatherine-houpt-vmd-phd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDr.%20Katherine%20Houpt%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20veterinary%20behaviorist%20and%20professor%20at%20the%20Cornell%20University%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20Medicine%20who%20specializes%20in%20domestic%20animal%20welfare%20and%20has%20studied%20the%20sleeping%20patterns%20of%20shelter%20dogs.%20%26quot%3BResilience%20is%20very%20important%2C''%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BDogs%20do%20not%20need%20or%20want%20to%20sleep%20on%20the%20linoleum.%20They%20need%20a%20cushioned%20but%20supportive%20surface.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20type%20of%20bed%20for%20a%20dog%20to%20sleep%20on%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20recommend%20a%20bed%20made%20of%20evenly%20supportive%20memory%20or%20orthopedic%20foam.%20Stuffed%20beds%20do%20not%20create%20uniform%20pressure%2C%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20soreness%20at%20pressure%20points%2C%20Wakshlag%20%3C%2Fspan%3Esays%3Cspan%3E.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Houpt%20recommends%20beds%20with%20bolsters.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20carefully%2C%20you%20will%20see%20they%20prefer%20to%20sleep%20with%20their%20backs%20against%20their%20owner%2C%20or%20against%20the%20back%20of%20the%20sofa%2C%20or%20even%20against%20the%20wall%2C''%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BThermoregulation%20is%20another%20big%20factor%2C%20and%20the%20dog%20does%20want%20to%20be%20in%20a%20warm%20place.%20That%20may%20be%20another%20reason%20they%20sleep%20with%20the%20back%20against%20something%2C%20to%20protect%20against%20drafts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat's%20the%20best%20type%20of%20bed%20for%20a%20dog%20with%20arthritis%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20orthopedic%20veterinarians%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvetmedbiosci.colostate.edu%2Fvth%2Fservices%2Forthopedic-medicine%2Farthritis-management-and-prrevention%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EColorado%20State%20University%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Cspan%3Ealleviating%20osteoarthritis%20in%20pets%20involves%20therapeutic%20forms%20of%20exercise%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eaddition%20to%20pain%20medications%20and%20weight%20management%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EWakshlag%20says%20recovery%3Cspan%3E%20from%20therapeutic%20exercise%20can%20be%20enhanced%20with%20the%20use%20of%20a%20supportive%20orthopedic%20dog%20bed%20that%20uses%20memory%20foam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20bed%20for%20a%20dog%20recovering%20from%20ACL%20surgery%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20right%20bed%20can%20help%20as%20a%20dog%20recovers%20from%20ACL%20surgery%2C%20says%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vet.cornell.edu%2Fresearch%2Ffaculty%2Fbrian-collins-dvm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDr.%20Brian%20Collins%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20senior%20lecturer%20in%20community%20practice%20service%20at%20Cornell%20University%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20Medicine.%20He%20recommends%20memory%20foam%20or%20something%20similar%20for%20stability%2C%20comfort%2C%20and%20support.%20This%20type%20of%20foam%20ensures%20a%20dog%20is%20comfortable%20while%20lying%20down%20but%20also%20stabilized%20when%20they%20step%20onto%20the%20bed%20or%20turn%20around.%20Bolsters%20can%20also%20provide%20physical%20support%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20security%2C%20and%20a%20place%20to%20rest%20their%20head.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20added%20stability%2C%20a%20nonskid%20bottom%20or%20at%20least%20placing%20the%20bed%20on%20a%20nonslip%20surface%20is%20important.%20%26quot%3BIt%20should%20be%20easy%20to%20get%20in%20and%20out%20of%20with%20a%20low%20border%20or%20an%20open%20side%20that%20the%20dog%20won't%20struggle%20to%20step%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20Collins%20says.%20%26quot%3BThe%20bed%20should%20be%20big%20enough%20for%20the%20dog%20to%20comfortably%20turn%20around%2C%20change%20position%2C%20and%20stretch%20out%20on.%26quot%3B%20In%20addition%2C%20he%20says%20a%20water-resistant%20bed%20that%20you%20can%20easily%20clean%20is%20essential%20for%20providing%20a%20clean%20environment%20while%20the%20incision%20heals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-orthopedic-dog-beds%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726696503000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eb47dad17aa3c7b2b40024%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-orthopedic-dog-beds%22%2C%22s