0so%20on%20a%20trip%20to%20Auckland%20in%202022%2C%20I%20planned%20a%20two-night%20getaway%20to%20the%20island.%20Take%20a%20look%20at%20what%20I%20discovered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOff%20the%20coast%20of%20New%20Zealand's%20capital%20is%20Waiheke%20Island%2C%20a%2036-square-mile%20island%20home%20to%20some%20of%20the%20country's%20wealthiest%20residents%20and%20vacationers.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bird's%20eye%20view%20of%20Waiheke%20Island%2C%20New%20Zealand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F637648f21f38cc0012877fdb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20bird's-eye%20view%20of%20Waiheke%20Island%2C%20New%20Zealand.%3Cp%3EFiona%20Ritchie%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20island%20is%20located%20in%20the%20Hauraki%20Gulf%20and%20has%20about%2010%2C000%20permanent%20residents.%20Many%20of%20those%20residents%20have%20familiar%20names%20and%20impressive%20titles%2C%20including%20New%20Zealand's%20richest%20man%2C%20Graeme%20Hart%2C%20and%20former%20All%20Blacks%20rugby%20coach%20Sir%20Graham%20Henry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20its%20permanent%20residents%2C%20Waiheke%20Island%20is%20also%20considered%20a%20vacation%20hot%20spot.%20About%203%2C500%20people%20own%20vacation%20homes%20on%20the%20island%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mansionglobal.com%2Farticles%2Fa-ferry-commute-from-auckland-waiheke-island-offers-sun-sand-and-wine-228186%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMansion%20Global%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20year%2C%20the%20rich%20and%20famous%20flock%20to%20those%20vacation%20homes%20to%20explore%20the%20island's%20wineries%2C%20pristine%20beaches%2C%20and%20dramatic%20landscapes.%20Waiheke%20has%20hosted%20everyone%20from%20Bill%20Gates%20to%20Madonna%20and%20Beyonc%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20the%20summer%20of%202022%2C%20I%20traveled%20to%20Waiheke%20to%20see%20what%20exactly%20entices%20affluent%20vacationers%20and%20residents%20to%20the%20island.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20view%20of%20Auckland%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20from%20a%20ferry.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6375521c09495900110e90da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20view%20of%20Auckland%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20from%20a%20ferry.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20rich%20vacationers%20often%20take%20private%20jets%20and%20boats%20to%20the%20island%2C%20that%20wasn't%20the%20case%20for%20me.%20Instead%2C%20I%20joined%20residents%20and%20visitors%20on%20a%2040-minute%20ferry%20ride%20from%20Auckland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ferry%20was%20my%20first%20indicator%20that%20the%20island%20is%20a%20place%20for%20the%20wealthy.%20My%20round-trip%20ticket%20on%20the%20Fullers360%20ferry%20cost%20%2450%2C%20and%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nzherald.co.nz%2Fnz%2Fcost-of-living-pushing-waiheke-locals-off-the-island%2FZ655FBU5Q5NXWD7IS2YZ77MN3M%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20Zealand%20Herald%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20public%20ferries%20in%20the%20world%20at%20the%20time%2C%20costing%20locals%20%24250%20monthly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20the%20ferry%20departed%20from%20Auckland%2C%20the%20city's%20harbor%20and%20Sky%20Tower%20faded%20into%20the%20distance.%20A%20little%20over%20half%20an%20hour%20later%2C%20a%20lush%2C%20green%20island%20speckled%20with%20homes%20came%20into%20view.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20ferry%20station%20in%20the%20Waiheke%20Island%20terminal.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6375526b2d22e7001161f6dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20ferry%20station%20in%20the%20Waiheke%20Island%20terminal.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20disembarked%20from%20the%20ferry%20and%20set%20out%20to%20explore%20Waiheke.%20Although%20the%20island%20is%2036%20square%20miles%2C%20the%20western%20half%20is%20more%20developed%2C%20with%20a%20concentration%20of%20wineries%20and%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20first%20stop%20was%20Mudbrick%20Vineyard%2C%20where%20I%20planned%20to%20do%20what%20Vogue%20says%20locals%2C%20tourists%2C%20and%20wealthy%20visitors%20do%20%E2%80%94%20sip%20wine.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20entrance%20to%20the%20Mudbrick%20Vineyard%20and%20Restaurant.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F637554392d22e7001161f77f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20entrance%20to%20the%20Mudbrick%20Vineyard%20and%20Restaurant.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWaiheke%20Island%20is%20home%20to%20more%20than%2030%20wineries%2C%20and%20thanks%20to%20the%20region's%20micro-climate%2C%20Syrah%20and%20Cabernet%20blends%20thrive%20in%20Waiheke's%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMudbrick%20Winery%20is%20one%20of%20the%20island's%20most%20popular%20places%20to%20taste%20these%20varieties.%20Celebrities%20like%20Taylor%20Swift%2C%20Eva%20Longoria%2C%20Cindy%20Crawford%2C%20and%20Shailene%20Woodley%20have%20all%20visited%20the%20vineyard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20I%20pulled%20into%20the%20parking%20lot%2C%20I%20understood%20why%20the%20winery%20entices%20such%20remarkable%20names.%20The%20vineyard%20had%20grand%20views%20overlooking%20Te%20Haruhi%20Bay.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Mudbrick%20vineyard.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6375555b09fde900119091b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Mudbrick%20Vineyard.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tasted%20six%20wines%2C%20which%20included%20Chardonnays%2C%20Syrahs%2C%20and%20red%20blends.%20It%20cost%20%2422.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wines%20had%20bold%20flavors%2C%20and%20I%20spent%20the%20afternoon%20wandering%20through%20the%20property's%20rows%20of%20vines%2C%20fields%20of%20lavender%2C%20and%20forests%20of%20fruit%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20visiting%20a%20celebrity-loved%20winery%2C%20I%20hoped%20to%20catch%20a%20glimpse%20of%20where%20the%20wealthy%20stay%20on%20Waiheke%20Island%2C%20too.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20real%20estate%20company%20advertises%20homes%20for%20sale%20on%20Waiheke%20Island.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63764c6c1f38cc00128780f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20real-estate%20company%20advertises%20homes%20for%20sale%20on%20Waiheke%20Island.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20won't%20find%20any%20Hiltons%2C%20Marriotts%2C%20or%20large%20hotels%20on%20Waiheke.%20There's%20a%20handful%20of%20boutique%20hotels%2C%20but%20most%20visitors%20book%20vacation%20homes%20for%20their%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDotted%20along%20the%20coast%20are%20these%20rental%20properties%2C%20many%20of%20which%20cost%20millions%20of%20dollars.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.realestate.co.nz%2Finsights%2Fauckland%2Fwaiheke-island%2Fwaiheke-island%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERealestate.co.nz%3C%2Fa%3E%20reports%20that%20the%20island's%20median%20asking%20price%20for%20a%20home%20was%20%242.5%20million%20this%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20real-estate%20prices%20have%20fluctuated%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20Waiheke%20is%20one%20of%20the%20places%20whe