had%20private%20entrances%2C%20tall%20hedges%2C%20and%20obstructed%20views%20of%20the%20properties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20my%20failed%20mansion%20mission%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20explore%20one%20of%20the%20island's%20pristine%20public%20beaches%20instead.%20I%20walked%20along%20Little%20Palm%20Beach%2C%20which%20is%20free%20to%20visit.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20entrance%20to%20Little%20Palm%20Beach%20on%20Waiheke%20Island%2C%20New%20Zealand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63754fe509495900110e9013%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20entrance%20to%20Little%20Palm%20Beach%20on%20Waiheke%20Island%2C%20New%20Zealand.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20beach%20was%20dotted%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20large%20homes%2C%20small%20abodes%2C%20and%20duplexes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%2C%20I%20met%20Chris%20McCarthny%2C%20an%20architect%20at%20Gulf%20Architects.%20We%20chatted%20about%20New%20Zealand%20food%20and%20his%20favorite%20wineries.%20He%20then%20pointed%20to%20a%20handful%20of%20mansions%20he%20designed%20along%20the%20rocky%20coast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcCarthny%20suggested%20I%20hike%20around%20Owhanake%20Bay.%20The%20cliffs%20there%2C%20he%20said%2C%20allow%20a%20better%20view%20of%20Waiheke's%20multimillion-dollar%20mansions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWith%20that%20in%20mind%2C%20I%20hopped%20in%20my%20car%20and%20headed%20to%20Owhanake%20Bay.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20parking%20lot%20at%20Owhanake%20Bay.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63754ef309495900110e8fba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20parking%20lot%20at%20Owhanake%20Bay%20on%20Waiheke%20Island%2C%20New%20Zealand.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20climbed%20up%20and%20through%20a%20forested%20area%2C%20the%20hiking%20trail%20led%20me%20to%20a%20freshly%20paved%20road%20that%20had%20a%20scattering%20of%20large%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThanks%20to%20the%20hike's%20high%20elevation%2C%20I%20spotted%20mansions%20Waiheke's%20rich%20and%20famous%20own.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20mansion%20along%20the%20hike.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63754e172d22e7001161f55f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20mansion%20along%20the%20hike.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20visitor%2C%20it%20was%20enticing%20to%20see%20these%20pricey%20homes%2C%20but%20after%20speaking%20with%20locals%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20these%20properties%2C%20over-tourism%2C%20and%20visitors%20like%20me%20have%20pushed%20permanent%20residents%20off%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Waiheke%20has%20the%20highest%20rate%20of%20homelessness%20per%20capita%20in%20the%20Auckland%20region%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsroom.co.nz%2F2024%2F08%2F17%2Ftourists-push-locals-out-of-waiheke-island%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENewsroom%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20the%20hike%2C%20I%20headed%20to%20my%20Airbnb%20for%20the%20evening.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20tiny%20house%20was%20tucked%20into%20the%20cliffside%20of%20Waiheke%20Island.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62e16e09536a23001911df6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20tiny%20house%20was%20tucked%20into%20the%20cliffside%20of%20Waiheke%20Island.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20staying%20on%20Waiheke%20I