ecome%20a%20medium%20for%20us%20to%20get%20engaged%20and%20get%20away%20from%20loneliness.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20world%20where%20time%20is%20a%20precious%20commodity%2C%20Beena%20emphasises%20that%20pursuing%20one%E2%80%99s%20passions%20not%20only%20enriches%20one%E2%80%99s%20life%20but%20also%20positively%20impacts%20several%20others.%20%E2%80%9CWhenever%20I%20met%20someone%20new%2C%20they%20would%20first%20ask%20my%20name%3B%20the%20second%20thing%20would%20be%20what%20I%20did%20for%20a%20living.%20Every%20person%20has%20a%20purpose.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20mine.%20These%20questions%20kept%20bothering%20me.%20But%20today%20as%20a%20working%20woman%20earning%20an%20income%2C%20my%20self-esteem%20has%20definitely%20grown.%20I%20feel%20confident%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20as%20we%20conclude%20our%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee.%20All%20photos%3A%20Beena%20Tom.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726662935000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fbees-of-beena-3-1726661514.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D366432%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kerala-based%20Beena%20Tom%20uses%20her%20cooking%20skills%20to%20make%20a%20variety%20of%20dishes%20from%20flowers%20and%20fruits%20available%20in%20her%20backyard%20%E2%80%93%20from%20coconut%2C%20arecanut%2C%20mangoes%2C%20guavas%2C%20to%20butterfly%20peas.%20Her%20passion%20led%20her%20to%20establish%20a%20thriving%20enterprise%20%E2%80%98Bees%20of%20Beena%E2%80%99%2C%20where%20she%20sells%20homemade%20jams%2C%20pickles%2C%20squash%2C%20juices%2C%20chips%2C%20and%20honey.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366432%2Fhomemade-food-pickles-jams-in-kerala-homemaker-runs-business-organic-garden-bees-of-beena%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%