%20spending%202.5%20years%20in%20Sitapur%20closely%20working%20with%20farmers%2C%20I%20saw%20the%20potential%20in%20something%20as%20small%20as%20a%20seed.%20We%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20massive%20impact%20by%20working%20for%20our%20farmers.%20Seeing%20their%20dedication%20first%20hand%20has%20been%20the%20most%20rewarding%20experience.%20Their%20hard%20work%20fuels%20our%20passion%20to%20turn%20our%20brand%20into%20a%20movement%20that%20not%20only%20improves%20health%20but%20also%20supports%20livelihoods%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Greenday.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726494464000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1725600771.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D364767%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lucknow-based%20Aishwarya%20Bhatnagar%20and%20Prateek%20Rastogi%20run%20Greenday%20to%20promote%20innovative%20farming%20methods%20and%20biofortified%20seeds%20that%20benefit%20both%20farmers%20and%20consumers%20alike.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20the%20Mumbai%20Mom%20Who%20Organises%20Nature%20Adventures%20for%20Parents%20%26amp%3B%20Children.%20Even%20Infants!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELast%20weekend%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20embarked%20on%20an%20exhilarating%20hike%20with%20our%201.5-year-old%20son.%20We%20set%20off%20at%205%20am%20to%20reach%20the%20village%20of%20Bhutivali%2C%20near%20Karjat.%20After%20enjoying%20breakfast%20at%20a%20local%E2%80%99s%20home%2C%20we%20began%20our%20trek%2C%20crossing%20a%20serene%20lake%20en%20route%20to%20a%20waterfall.%20The%20sight%20of%20the%20picturesque%20lake%20was%20a%20true%20feast%20for%20the%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20took%20turns%20carrying%20our%20son%2C%20a%20light%20drizzle%20energised%20us.%20After%20nearly%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%2C%20we%20reached%20the%20waterfall%20and%20knew%20the%20effort%20was%20well%20worth%20it.%20Watching%20our%20son%20delight%20in%20the%20water%2C%20chase%20butterflies%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F325192%2Fsaakshi-gulati-nikita-mathur-travel-with-kids-india-plan-vacations-for-moms-kids-toddlers-baby%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplay%20with%20other%20children%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereminded%20us%20that%20some%20experiences%20are%20priceless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20enjoying%20some%20hot%20Maggi%20and%20tea%20near%20the%20waterfall%2C%20we%20started%20our%20return%20journey%2C%20only%20to%20be%20greeted%20by%20a%20herd%20of%20cows%20and%20buffaloes.%20Our%20son%20was%20completely%20captivated%2C%20sitting%20and%20watching%20them%20for%20several%20minutes.%20We%20eventually%20had%20to%20coax%20him%20away%20with%20a%20promise%20to%20bring%20him%20back!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20returned%20home%20that%20evening%2C%20our%20hearts%20full%20and%20our%20pockets%20brimming%20with%20unforgettable%20memories%2C%20realising%20what%20we%20had%20been%20missing%20all%20along.%20Our%20son%20had%20made%20new%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20hens%2C%20cows%2C%20butterflies%2C%20and%20swans%20%E2%80%94%20and%20those%20simple%20moments%20made%20the%20day%20truly%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20increasingly%20digital%20world%20where%20children%20are%20often%20glued%20to%20screens%2C%20introducing%20them%20to%20nature%20has%20never%20been%20more%20important.%20Nehal%20Shah%20realised%20this%20after%20becoming%20a%20mother.%20As%20an%20avid%20trekker%2C%20she%20sought%20out%20places%20and%20trips%20suitable%20for%20her%20infant%2C%20but%20her%20searches%20only%20led%20to%20indoor%20activities.%20Frustrated%20by%20the%20lack%20of%20outdoor%20options%20for%20young%20children%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20create%20something%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5