na%20chips%2C%20pickles%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Epodis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spice%20powders)%2C%20which%20made%20cooking%20a%20meal%20very%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-women-1726037821.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20women%20of%20Tocco%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-women-1726037821.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-women-1726037821-300x168.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-women-1726037821-500x280.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-women-1726037821-768x431.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-women-1726037821-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365471%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22718%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20women%20of%20Tocco.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20a%20consistent%20and%20convenient%20supply%20of%20food%20that%20reminded%20me%20of%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20Reshma%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20hectic%20schedule%20coupled%20with%20late%20nights%20led%20to%20lots%20of%20restaurant%20meals.%20A%20few%20years%20later%2C%20Reshma%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20PCOS%20(Polycystic%20Ovary%20Syndrome).%20This%20diagnosis%20triggered%20her%20search%20for%20healthier%2C%20authentic%2C%20home-cooked%20regional%20food.%20Unfortunately%2C%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20anything%20like%20it%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20sister%2C%20Annu%2C%20who%20lived%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20faced%20the%20same%2